0said%20something%2C%26quot%3B%20Elon%20Musk%20told%20Isaacson.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20it%20was%20only%20by%20reading%20books%20that%20I%20began%20to%20learn%20that%20people%20did%20not%20always%20say%20what%20they%20really%20meant.%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20%26quot%3Bhad%20a%20preference%20for%20things%20that%20were%20more%20precise%20such%20as%20engineering%2C%20physics%2C%20and%20coding%2C%26quot%3B%20Isaacson%20writes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMaye%20Musk%20told%20Isaacson%20that%20Elon%20Musk%20%26quot%3Bbecame%20so%20lonely%20and%20sad%2C%26quot%3B%20when%20he%20started%20going%20to%20school.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BKimbal%20and%20Tosca%20would%20make%20friends%20on%20the%20first%20day%20and%20bring%20them%20home%2C%20but%20Elon%20never%20brought%20friends%20home.%20He%20wanted%20to%20have%20friends%2C%20but%20just%20didn't%20know%20how.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-biography-followed-sister-clubs-parties-lonely-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EElon%20Musk%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20a%20teenager%2C%20his%20family%20briefly%20lived%20in%20Toronto%2C%20and%20he%20insisted%20on%20following%20his%20sister%20Tosca%20Musk%20around%20to%20clubs%20and%20parties%20so%20he%20didn't%20have%20to%20be%20lonely%2C%20according%20to%20the%20book.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETosca%20Musk%2C%20%26quot%3Ba%20saucy%20teenager%2C%26quot%3B%20liked%20to%20go%20out%20often%20and%20allowed%20her%20brother%20to%20join%20her%20but%20ordered%20him%20to%20%26quot%3Bstay%2010%20feet%20away%2C%26quot%3B%20from%20her%20%26quot%3Bat%20all%20times.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20walked%20%26quot%3Bbehind%20her%20and%20her%20friends%2C%26quot%3B%20Isaacson%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3Bcarrying%20a%20book%20to%20read%20whenever%20they%20went%20into%20a%20club%20or%20party.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%