%20%E2%80%9Cacted%20in%20breach%E2%80%9D%20of%20various%20sections%20of%20the%20Financial%20Services%20Act%2C%20the%20Securities%20Act%2C%20the%20Financial%20Intelligence%20and%20Anti-Money%20Laundering%20Regulations%20(2003%20and%202018)%20and%20the%20Code%20on%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Money%20Laundering%20and%20Terrorist%20Financing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20licence%20revocation%20notice%20is%20on%20the%20regulator%E2%80%99s%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThese%20alleged%20breaches%20relate%20to%20non-compliance%20on%20maintaining%20records%20of%20clients%20and%20transactions%2C%20accounting%20and%20auditing%20standards%3B%20safeguards%20against%20dummy%20officers%3B%20corporate%20governance%20and%20the%20prescribed%20internal%20mechanism%20to%20identify%20risks%20of%20money%20laundering%20and%20terrorist%20financing%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Cem%3EIE%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEIFM%20was%20held%20guilty%20of%20breaching%20both%20the%202003%20and%202018%20versions%20of%20Mauritius%E2%80%99s%20Financial%20Intelligence%20and%20Anti-Money%20Laundering%20Regulations%2C%20the%20report%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20last%20available%20records%2C%20during%20March-April%202018%2C%20EIFM%E2%80%99s%20two%20Mauritius%20funds%20held%203.9%25%20of%20Adani%20Power%20Limited%2C%203.86%25%20of%20Adani%20Transmission%20Limited%2C%20and%2C%20at%20least%2C%201.73%25%20of%20Adani%20Enterprise%20Limited.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20FSC%20told%3Cem%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noamphtml%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2F%5C%22%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3A%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20a%20licence%20is%20revoked%2C%20it%20is%20on%20a%20permanent%20basis.%20Following%20the%20revocation%E2%80%A6%20licensees%20are%20directed%20to%20initiate%20the%20necessary%20actions%20for%20the%20orderly%20dissolution%20of%20their%20business%20and%20the%20discharge%20of%20their%20liabilities.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20the%20implication%20of%20the%20revocation%20of%20EIFM%E2%80%99s%20licences%2C%20an%20Adani%20Group%20spokesperson%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CWe%20will%20not%20be%20able%20to%20comment%20on%20matters%20pertaining%20to%20independent%20individual%20shareholders.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20news%20assumes%20significance%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ft.com%2Fcontent%2F8d46b435-9725-46d4-80be-2cb3e276c4c9%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EFinancial%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20claimed%20funds%20from%20unknown%20sources%20were%20channelled%20by%20two%20British%20Virgin%20Islands%20shell%20companies%20%E2%80%93%20United%20Arab%20Emirates%20national%20Nasser%20Ali%20Shaban%20Adil%E2%80%99s%20Gulf%20Asia%20Trade%20and%20Investment%20Limited%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noamphtml%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fexplained%2Fexplained-global%2Fexplained-china-problem-nancy-pelosi-visit-taiwan-8066503%2F%5C%22%3ETaiwan%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0national%20Chang%20Cung-Ling%E2%80%99s%20Lingo%20Investment%20Limited%20%E2%80%94%20through%20the%20Emerging%20India%20Focus%20Funds%20(Mauritius)%20and%20the%20EM%20Resurgent%20Fund%20(Mauritius)%20under%20the%20Global%20Opportunities%20Fund%20(Bermuda).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Cem%3EFT%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20both%20these%20individuals%20were%20associates%20of%20Adani%20Group%20chairperson%20Gautam%20Adani%E2%80%99s%20brother%20Vinod%20Adani.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20the%20Pandora%20Papers%20investigation%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fpandora-papers-confirm-adani-groups-connection-to-shell-companies-named-in-reports%5C%22%3Erevealed%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20these%20two%20shell%20companies%20registered%20in%20the%20BVI%20were%20indeed%20connected%20to%20the%20Adani%20Group.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20as%20per%20SEBI%20records%2C%20under%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Money%20Laundering%20Act%2C%20Emerging%20India%20Fo