0require%20borrowers%20to%20waive%20their%20rights%20to%20bring%20a%20class%20action%20lawsuit.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20students%20might%20not%20even%20have%20to%20graduate%20before%20they%20find%20themselves%20facing%20abusive%20debt%20collection%20practices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Thursday%2C%20the%20Consumer%20Financial%20Protection%20Bureau%20released%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.consumerfinance.gov%2Fabout-us%2Fnewsroom%2Fcfpb-report-finds-college-tuition-payment-plans-can-put-student-borrowers-at-risk%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%20highlighting%20a%20risky%20agreement%20nearly%204%20million%20students%20sign%20up%20for%20each%20term%3A%20tuition%20payment%20plans%20offered%20by%20their%20school.%20It%20seems%20innocent%20on%20the%20surface%20%E2%80%94%20a%20student%20can%20sign%20up%20for%20a%20plan%20that%20would%20allow%20them%20to%20spread%20the%20upfront%20cost%20of%20their%20tuition%20into%20typically%20three%20to%20six%20interest-free%20payments%20so%20those%20who%20cannot%20afford%20to%20make%20the%20entirety%20of%20the%20payment%20can%20still%20attend%20classes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20when%20the%20CFPB%20dug%20deeper%2C%20it%20found%20the%20payment%20agreements%20have%20confusing%2C%20and%20potentially%20illegal%2C%20terms%20and%20debt%20collection%20practices.%20Students%20who%20miss%20just%20one%20payment%20could%20end%20up%20with%20hundreds%20of%20dollars%20in%20late%20fees%2C%20their%20meal%20plans%20could%20be%20stripped%20away%2C%20and%20they%20could%20be%20kicked%20out%20of%20their%20classes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20data-block-key%3D%5C%22ptfc%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BTuition%20payment%20plans%20offered%20by%20schools%20may%20look%20like%20a%20good%20option%2C%20but%20this%20report%20shows%20student%20borrowers%20can%20end%20up%20paying%20high%20fees%2C%20be%20forced%20to%20sign%20away%20their%20legal%20rights%2C%20or%20even%20have%20their%20transcript%20withheld%20by%20their%20school%2C%26quot%3B%20CFPB%20Director%20Rohit%20Chopra%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%20%26quot%3BColleges%20and%20universities%20should%20take%20a%20hard%20look%20at%20their%20repayment%20plans%20and%20avoid%20subjecting%20borrowers%20to%20high%20fees%20or%20coercive%20debt%20collection%20practices.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20data-block-key%3D%5C%22ptfc%5C%22%3EThe%20report%20analyzed%20450%20institutions'%20payment%20plans%20%E2%80%94%2060%25%20of%20which%20outsourced%20management%20of%20the%20payment%20plans%20to%20third-party%20financial%20service%20providers%2C%20and%20it%20found%20that%20the%20interest-fee%20plans%20aren't%20as%20affordable%20as%20they%20sound.%20Within%20the%20sample%2C%2089%25%20of%20schools%20charged%20an%20enrollment%20fee%20that%20could%20be%20as%20high%20as%20%24250%20and%2044%25%20charged%20late%20fees%20averaging%20%2446%2C%20with%20one%20school%20charging%20%24300%20for%20a%20student's%20first%20late%20payment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20data-block-key%3D%5C%22ptfc%5C%22%3EThe%20CFPB%20also%20found%20that%20in%20some%20cases%2C%20consequences%20of%20missing%20a%20payment%20are%20not%20even%20disclosed%20in%20the%20contract%2C%20meaning%20borrowers%20might%20have%20no%20idea%20of%20the%20fees%20they%20could%20accumulate%20if%20they%20fall%20behind%20on%20the%20plan.%20In%20the%20event%20of%20a%20missed%20payment%2C%20colleges%20could%20send%20students%20to%20collections%20and%20their%20credit%20scores%20could%20take%20a%20hit.%20At%20that%20point%2C%20the%20student%20might%20not%20have%20any%20legal%20protection%20because%20some%20payment%20plans%20require%20the%20student%20to%20waive%20their%20rights%20to%20participate%20in%20any%20class%20action%20lawsuit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20data-block-key%3D%5C%22ptfc%5C%22%3EOne%20student%20told%20the%20CFPB%20that%20their%20federal%20loans%20and%20grants%20did%20not%20cover%20their%20tuition%20payment%2C%20so%20their%20school%20demanded%20the%20student%20pay%20them%20in%20full%20or%20enroll%20in%20a%20payment%20plan%20that%20would%20subject%20them%20to%20late%20fees.%20%26quot%3BIf%20I%20did%20not%20do%20this%20I%20was%20told%20my%20classes%20would%20be%20dropped.%20I%20do%20not%20believe%20this%20is%20fair%20and%20have%20never%20been%20subject%20to%20this%20in%20past%20year%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20student%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-block-key%3D%5C%22ptfc%5C%22%3EWhat%20happens%20to%20students%20who%20miss%20tuition%20plan%20payments%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20late%20fees%20are%20just%20the%20start.%20Once%20a%20student%20misses%20a%20payment%2C%20they%20are%20subjected%20to%20aggressive%20debt%20collection%20practices%2C%20and%20confusing%20terms%20in%20the%20payment%20agreement%20could%20leave%20the%20student%20without%20any%20legal%20protections.%20The%20report%20said%20that%20in%20some%20cases%2C%20borrowers%20might%20even%20be%20unknowingly%20signed%20up%20for%20a%20tuition%20payment%20plan%20if%20their%20federal%20student%20aid%20is%20not%20enough%20to%20cover%20the%20full%20tuition%20cost.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20these%20situations%20occur%2C%20the%20use%20of%20the%20product%20could%20lead%20to%20fees%20and%20financial%20difficulties%20for%20students%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20the%20inconsistency%20among%20payment%20plans%20can%20leave%20students%20facing%20disparate%20consequences%20for%20missing%20a%20payment.%20For%20example%2C%20a%20student%20with%20a%20loan%20of%20%24525%20could%20end%20up%20paying%20between%20%2469%20and%20%24399%20in%20fees%2C%20based%20on%20the%20CFPB's%20sample%20%E2%80%94%20and%20it%20could%20leave%20the%20student%20owing%20more%20than%20they%20originally%20borrowed%20to%20finance%20their%20education.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221304%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22CFPB%20example%20of%20late%20fees%20on%20tuition%20payment%20plans.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F650477f1b8708d001927d426%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22478%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECFPB%20example%20of%20late%20fees%20on%20tuition%20payment%20plans.%3Cp%3EConsumer%20Financial%20Protection%20Bureau%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFollowing%20a%20missed%20payment%2C%20the%20school%20could%20have%20the%20authority%20to%20withhold%20a%20student's%20transcript%2C%20which%20could%20prevent%20the%20student%20from%20moving%20to%20a%20different%20school%20or%20getting%20a%20job.%20The%20CFPB%20also%20found%20that%20some%20schools%20penalized%20students%20for%20missing%20payments%20by%20deactivating%20their%20campus%20cards%2C%20along%20with%20%26quot%3Bdismissal%20of%20students%20from%20residence%20halls%2C%20suspension%20of%20meals%20plans%2C%20and%20suspension%20of%20participation%20on%20athletic%20teams%2C%20along%20with%20late%20fee%20charges%20and%20interest%20charged%20on%20unpaid%20balances%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20CFPB%20said%20it%20will%20continue%20to%20monitor%20schools'%20payment%20plans%20to%20ensure%20they%20are%20in%20accordance%20with%20consumer%20law.%20Beyond%20predatory%20behavior%20while%20a%20borrower%20is%20in%20school%2C%20President%20Joe%20Biden's%20administration%20has%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-debt-bankruptcy-relief-companies-ignoring-court-orders-loan-forgiveness-2023-3%5C%22%3Escrutinized%3C%2Fa%3E%20other%20potentially%20abusive%20and%20misleading%20behavior%20that%20could%20impact%20both%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-forgiveness-private-debt-no-relief-interest-rates-payments-2023-8%5C%22%3Eprivate%20and%20federal%20borrowers%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20including%20scams%20related%20to%20federal%20student-loan%20forgiveness.%20With%20the%20higher%20education%20industry%20undergoing%20a%20series%20of%20changes%20right%20now%2C%20the%20CFPB%20and%20Education%20Department%20have%20encouraged%20borrowers%20to%20be%20extra%20vigilant%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.