C%20scientists%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20known%20hybrid%20of%20a%20dog%20and%20a%20fox%20has%20been%20discovered%20in%20the%20wild%20after%20being%20hit%20by%20a%20car%20in%20Brazil.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20animal%2C%20nicknamed%20dog-fox%2C%20was%20found%20after%20it%20was%20taken%20to%20a%20vet%20in%202021%2C%20and%20hospital%20staff%20could%20not%20determine%20what%20it%20was%2C%20the%20British%20newspaper%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraph.co.uk%2Fnews%2F2023%2F09%2F13%2Ffirst-dog-fox-hybrid-discovered-in-wild-brazil%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Telegraph%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EScientists%20studied%20the%20animal's%20genes%20and%20revealed%20in%20a%20recently%20published%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC10417603%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estudy%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20animal's%20mother%20was%20a%20pampas%20fox.%20Her%20father%20was%20a%20domestic%20dog%20of%20an%20unspecified%20breed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EView%20a%20photo%20of%20the%20unique%20animal%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraph.co.uk%2Fcontent%2Fdam%2Fnews%2F2023%2F09%2F13%2FTELEMMGLPICT000349112189_16946140959410_trans_NvBQzQNjv4BqU0Gp0xmgZ8A1_PX6_7t4tUWy_sGK6oioMu5BzggyGUY.jpeg%3Fimwidth%3D960%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20dog-fox%20resembles%20both%20a%20dog%20and%20a%20fox%20and%20shares%20characteristics%20with%20both%20animals%2C%20scientists%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20refused%20food%20and%20preferred%20live%20rodents%2C%20barked%20like%20a%20dog%20but%20had%20a%20thick%20coat%20of%20hair%20similar%20to%20a%20fox%2C%20and%20was%20initially%20cautious%20of%20humans%20but%20would%20eventually%20warm%20to%20them%2C%20per%20The%20Telegraph.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFl%C3%A1via%20Ferrari%2C%20a%20conservationist%20who%20worked%20with%20the%20animal%2C%20told%20The%20Telegraph%20that%20she%20was%20an%20%26quot%3Bamazing%20animal.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20not%20as%20docile%20as%20a%20dog%2C%20but%20it%20also%20lacked%20the%20aggressiveness%20expected%20of%20a%20wild%20canid%20when%20handled%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20had%20a%20shy%20and%20cautious%20personality%2C%20generally%20preferring%20to%20stay%20away%20from%20people.%20Over%20the%20time%20she%20was%20hospitalized%20for%20treatment%2C%20I%20believe%20she%20started%20to%20feel%20safer.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20she%20started%20to%20feel%20comfortable%2C%20she%20occasionally%20allowed%20herself%20to%20be%20touched%20and%20caressed%20and%20sometimes%20even%20played%20with%20toys%2C%20Ferrari%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20names%20suggested%20for%20the%20animal%20were%20%26quot%3Bgraxorra%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bdogxim%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20reference%20the%20Portuguese%20names%20for%20the%20pampas%20fox%20and%20female%20dog.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20type%20of%20hybridization%20between%20species%20from%20different%20genera%20is%20relatively%20rare%20and%20has%20not%20been%20previously%20documented%20in%20South%20America.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20there%20have%20previously%20been%20recorded%20cases%20of%20hybridization%20between%20domestic%20dogs%20and%20wild%20canids%20%E2%80%93%20a%20family%20of%20mammals%20that%20includes%20wolves%20and%20foxes%20%E2%80%93%20this%20was%20the%20first%20case%20of%20these%20two%20specific%20species%20cross-breeding%20and%20the%20first%20on%20the%20continent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20our%20study%2C%20we%20recorded%20the%20first%20case%20of%20hybridization%20between%20one%20species%20of%20wild%20canid%20and%20the%20domestic%20dog%2C%26quot%3B%20study%20author%20Bruna%20Elenara%20Szynwelski%2C%20a%20PhD%20student%20in%20genetics%20and%20molecular%20biology%20at%20Universidade%20Federal%20do%20Rio%20Grande%20do%20Sul%2C%20told%20The%20Telegraph.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%2C%20different%20to%20cases%20of%20hybridization%20studied%20in%20North%20America%2C%20Europe%2C%20and%20Africa%2C%20this%20hybridization%20occurred%20between%20species%20from%20the%20distinct%20genera%3A%20lycalopex%20and%20canis.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20type%20of%20hybridization%20can%20threaten%20wildlife%20conservation%20due%20to%20risks%20of%20introgression%20and%20disease%20transmission%20by%20the%20dog%2C%20the%20study%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20dog-fox%20was%20neutered%20as%20part%20of%20her%20treatment%2C%20so%20it%20is%20not%20clear%20whether%20she%20could%20reproduce%2C%20but%20scientists%20believe%20it%20would%20be%20possible%2C%20The%20Telegraph%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20animal%20recovered%20at%20the%20veterinary%20hospital%20of%20the%20Universidade%20Federal%20do%20Rio%20Grande%20do%20Sul%20and%20was%20then%20transferred%20to%20conservation%20center%20Mantenedouro%20S%C3%A3o%20Braz%20in%20Santa%20Maria%20city%2C%20per%20The%20Telegraph.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdog-fox-hybrid-discovered-brazil-hit-by-car-2023-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694857547000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65046955b8708d001927b9e7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdog-fox-hybrid-discovered-brazil-hit-by-car-2023-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22After%20the%20animal%20was%20hit%20by%20a%20car%20in%20Brazil%2C%20scientists%20struggled%20to%20determine%20whether%20it%20was%20a%20dog%20or%20a%20fox.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ashoaib%40insider.com%20(Alia%20Shoaib)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A19%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdog-fox-hybrid-discovered-brazil-hit-by-car-2023-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Imran%20Khan%20files%20petition%20in%20Islamabad%20court%2C%20seeks%20post-arrest%20bail%20in%20cipher%20case%22%2C%22c