%20buffett%20serious%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F59108c04dd089544778b4ca1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221833%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWarren%20Buffett.%3Cp%3EDrew%20Angerer%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EWarren%20Buffett%20invested%20a%20vital%20%243%20billion%20in%20Dow%20Chemical%20at%20the%20height%20of%20the%20financial%20crisis.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIn%20return%2C%20Berkshire%20Hathaway%20received%20preferred%20stock%20paying%20a%20yearly%20dividend%20of%208.5%25.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBuffett's%20company%20ultimately%20made%20an%20estimated%20%243%20billion%20profit%20from%20stock%20sales%20and%20dividends.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWarren%20Buffett%20poured%20%243%20billion%20into%20Dow%20Chemical%20in%20the%20depths%20of%20the%20financial%20crisis%2C%20helping%20the%20manufacturer%20to%20complete%20an%20acquisition%20at%20a%20time%20when%20investors%2C%20lenders%2C%20and%20companies%20were%20taking%20cover.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20the%20story%20of%20one%20of%20Buffett's%20signature%20deals%2C%20which%20provided%20much-needed%20cash%20to%20an%20ailing%20company%20%E2%80%93%20and%20earned%20him%20a%20healthy%20return.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EFinancial%20chemistry%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDow%20agreed%20to%20buy%20Rohm%20and%20Haas%20for%20nearly%20%2419%20billion%20including%20debt%20in%20July%202008%2C%20and%20roped%20in%20Warren%20Buffett's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Fbrk-b-stock%5C%22%3EBerkshire%20Hathaway%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20help%20with%20the%20financing.%20The%20acquisition%20was%20part%20of%20Dow's%20strategy%20to%20shift%20its%20focus%20away%20from%20bulk%20chemicals%20toward%20higher-margin%2C%20specialty%20chemicals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBuffett%20agreed%20to%20put%20up%20%243%20billion%20in%20exchange%20for%203%20million%20Series%20A%20convertible%20preferred%20shares%2C%20which%20paid%20an%208.5%25%20dividend%2C%20or%20%24255%20million%20a%20year.%20Preferred%20shares%20often%20offer%20larger%20dividends%20than%20common%20shares%2C%20and%20holders%20take%20priority%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20dividend%20payouts.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDow%20had%20the%20option%20to%20convert%20some%20or%20all%20of%20Berkshire's%20preferred%20stock%20into%20common%20stock%20starting%20in%20April%202014%2C%20at%20a%20ratio%20of%2024.201%20common%20shares%20for%20each%20preferred%20share.%20The%20maker%20of%20chemicals%2C%20plastics%2C%20agroscience%20products%2C%20and%20advanced%20materials%20could%20only%20do%20so%20if%20its%20stock%20price%20exceeded%20%2453.72%20for%2020%20trading%20days%20in%20a%2030-day%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EAdverse%20reaction%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDow's%20takeover%20proved%20to%20be%20poorly%20timed.%20Lehman%20Brothers%20collapsed%20two%20months%20later%2C%20causing%20credit%20markets%20to%20seize%20up%2C%20asset%20prices%20to%20plunge%2C%20and%20shockwaves%20to%20reverberate%20through%20the%20housing%20market%20and%20the%20wider%20US%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20chemicals%20giant%20had%20planned%20to%20cover%20a%20big%20chunk%20of%20the%20deal's%20cost%20using%20%249%20billion%20of%20proceeds%20from%20a%20joint%20venture%20with%20Kuwait's%20Petrochemical%20Industries.%20However%2C%20the%20state-run%20company%20scrapped%20the%20partnership%20in%20December%202008%2C%20sending%20Dow%20stock%20plunging.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20world%20fell%20apart%2C%26quot%3B%20Buffett%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbuffett.cnbc.com%2Fvideo%2F2017%2F02%2F27%2Fbuffett-buys-airlines-and-apple-full-interview.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%20CNBC%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202017%2C%20recalling%20that%20Dow%20tried%20and%20failed%20to%20back%20out%20of%20acquiring%20Rohm%20and%20Haas.%20%26quot%3BWe%20closed%20the%20deal%20to%20buy%20the%20stock%20in%20April%202009%2C%20by%20which%20time%20the%20market%20had%20totally%20disintegrated.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EG