s%20that%20popped%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDuring%20that%20whole%20period%2C%20we%20had%20these%20commitments%20and%20that%20kept%20me%20from%20doing%20some%20other%20things%20we%20might%20have%20done%20at%20that%20time%20%E2%80%94%20the%20fact%20that%20we%20had%20this%20%243%20billion%20going%20out%20the%20door%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20CNBC%2C%20referring%20to%20Berkshire's%20investment%20in%20Dow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20Dow%2C%20Buffett's%20money%20and%20vote%20of%20confidence%20helped%20to%20assuage%20fear%20on%20Wall%20Street%20that%20the%20company%20had%20bitten%20off%20more%20than%20it%20could%20chew%20and%20might%20tumble%20into%20insolvency.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20stake%20was%20taken%20at%20a%20time%20when%20Dow%20was%20really%20desperate%2C%26quot%3B%20Hassan%20Ahmed%2C%20an%20analyst%20at%20Alembic%20Global%20Advisors%20at%20the%20time%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-dowchemical-buffett-idUSTRE6A93WC20101110%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%20Reuters%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202010.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBuffett%20may%20have%20felt%20he%20massively%20overpaid%2C%20but%20the%20deal%20he%20negotiated%20was%20still%20lucrative.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThose%20preferred%20shares%20are%20yielding%20a%20lot%2C%26quot%3B%20Ahmen%20said.%20%26quot%3BPurely%20on%20a%20financial%20basis%2C%20I'd%20like%20to%20knock%20him%20out.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EProducing%20profit%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDow%20paid%20supersized%20dividends%20to%20Buffett%20for%20more%20than%20seven%20years.%20In%20December%202016%2C%20it%20finally%20converted%20Berkshire's%20preferred%20shares%20into%2072.6%20million%20common%20shares%2C%20freeing%20itself%20from%20the%20costly%20commitment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBuffett%20and%20his%20team%20had%20no%20interest%20in%20owning%20Dow's%20common%20stock%2C%20so%20they%20sold%20all%20of%20the%20shares%20they%20were%20set%20to%20receive%20ahead%20of%20time.%20Dow%20rede