%20that%20writing%20to%20AI%2C%20Price%20told%20Insider.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWedding%20vows%20in%20the%20ChatGPT%20age%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EA%20few%20months%20ago%2C%20Price%20began%20testing%20out%20AI%20tools%20like%20Open%20AI's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feverything-you-need-to-know-about-chat-gpt-2023-1%5C%22%3EChatGPT%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20Writer's%20Block%20Assistant%2C%20a%20free%20content-creation%20tool%20launched%20in%20March%20by%20Joy%2C%20a%20wedding%20platform%20that%20allows%20couples%20to%20design%20wedding%20websites%2C%20invitations%2C%20and%20build%20a%20registry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPrice%20is%20now%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-ai-chatbots-like-chatgpt-work-explainer-2023-7%5C%22%3Eusing%20ChatGPT%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0and%20Joy's%20AI%20assistant%20to%20write%20the%20vows%20she'll%20recite%20to%20Sorensen%20on%20their%20wedding%20day.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20mean%2C%20we've%20been%20together%20for%20a%20while.%20We've%20been%20through%20a%20lot%2C%20so%20there's%20a%20lot%20of%20things%20that%20I%20want%20to%20include%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20kind%20of%20a%20Frankenstein%20culmination%20for%20me.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe's%20using%20the%20Writer's%20Block%20Assistant%20to%20generate%20the%20initial%20text.%20Unlike%20ChatGPT%2C%20which%20is%20designed%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-researchers-jailbreak-bard-chatgpt-safety-rules-2023-7%5C%22%3Efield%20an%20unlimited%20set%20of%20questions%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Price%20prefers%20Joy's%20AI%20assistant%20as%20a%20starting%20point%20because%20it%20offers%20a%20structured%20set%20of%20questions%20about%20the%20content%20of%20the%20vows%20and%20the%20tone.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22815%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Molly%20Price%20vows%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64cac2a695fe1f0019df6286%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22611%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJoy%20says%20that%20the%20Wedding%20Writer's%20Block%20Assistant%20says%20it%20helps%20users%20generate%20%26quot%3Bwedding-related%20wordage.%26quot%3B%20Here's%20an%20example%20of%20what%20Price%20put%20into%20the%20tool.%3Cp%3EJoy%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20tool%20is%20accessible%20via%20Joy's%20website%20and%20uses%C2%A0OpenAI's%20technology%20to%20draft%20%26quot%3Bwedding-related%20wordage%26quot%3B%20as%20the%20company%20describes%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUsers%20input%20the%20type%20of%20text%20they're%20looking%20for%20help%20with%2C%20whether%20that's%20their%20vows%2C%20a%20love%20story%20for%20their%20wedding%20website%2C%20or%20even%20thank-you%20notes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20they're%20asked%20to%20enter%20information%20about%20the%20context%2C%20or%20the%20story%20it%20will%20highlight%2C%20and%20their%20preferred%20style%20of%20writing.%20The%20style%20options%20are%20as%20benign%20as%20%26quot%3Ba%20friend%2C%26quot%3B%20as%20esoteric%20as%20the%20poet%20Rumi%2C%20or%20as%20salty%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bpessimistic%20ex.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20Price%20is%20running%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftired-ai-writing-tools-and-chatgpt-is-the-best-2023-7%5C%22%3Etext%20through%20ChatGPT%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20add%20humor%2C%20voice%2C%20and%20color.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20use%20ChatGPT%20to%20kind%20of%20change%20the%20tone-of-voice%20and%20make%20it%20a%20little%20less%20robotic.%20which%20is%20weird%20because%20it's%20coming%20from%20AI%2C%26quot%3B%20Price%20said.%20She%20added%20that%20ChatGPT%20also%20offers%20more%20facility%20with%20editing%20text%2C%20whether%20that's%20by%20pointing%20out%20sections%20to%20cut%2C%20or%20suggesting%20areas%20that%20could%20use%20more%20details.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWedding%20stress%20relief%20%E2%80%94%20powered%20by%20ChatGPT%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20tools%20have%20helped%20Price%20streamline%20her%20thoughts%2C%20and%20turn%20them%20into%20a%20written%20product%2C%20which%20has%20also%20eased%20some%20of%20her%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fwhat-wedding-planner-thinks-guests-should-do-stop-doing%5C%22%3Ewedding%20planning%3C%2Fa%3E%20anxiety.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEssentially%2C%20to%20me%2C%20coming%20up%20with%20a%20speech%20felt%20like%20having%20a%20big%20research%20paper%2C%20so%20it%20definitely%20took%20the%20stress%20away%20from%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Price%20said.%20She%20later%20told%20Insider%20by%20email%20that%20words%20aren't%20her%20strong%20suit%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F5-activities-at-home-to-become-a-stronger-public-speaker-2020-3%5C%22%3Eespecially%20in%20front%20of%20a%20crowd%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22897%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Molly%20Price%20vows%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64cac47095fe1f0019df656e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22673%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJoy%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20Price%20is%20apparently%20not%20alone.%20According%20to%20an%20online%20questionnaire%20Joy%20conducted%20in%20February%20through%20its%20Instagram%20story%20that%20surveyed%20more%201%2C350%20people%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0%20both%20users%20and%20non-users%20of%20the%20platform%20%E2%80%94%2089%25%20of%20respondents%20found%20it%20%26quot%3Bsomewhat%20overwhelming%26quot%3B%20to%20begin%20writing%20their%20wedding%20materials.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20exactly%20a%20scientific%20look%20at%20the%20issue%2C%20but%20still%2C%2057%25%20said%20they%20would%20consider%20using%20an%20AI%20assistant%20like%20ChatGPT%20to%20jumpstart%20the%20writing%20process%20for%20wedding%20materials.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPrice%20said%20that%20without%20the%20AI%20tools%2C%20she%20would%20have%20just%20gotten%20up%20and%20s