20coming%20back.%20Healthcare%20is%20one%20reason%20why.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Amanda%20Rollins%20in%20front%20of%20the%20Seine%20and%20Eiffel%20Tower%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65030937992da60019ec3fa6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222625%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAmanda%20Rollins%20in%20front%20of%20the%20Seine%20and%20Eiffel%20Tower%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Amanda%20Rollins%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAmanda%20Rollins%2C%2034%2C%20moved%20from%20Massachusetts%20to%20Paris%20six%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAfter%20experiencing%20the%20food%2C%20free%20healthcare%2C%20and%20a%20lower%20cost%20of%20living%2C%20she%20doesn't%20plan%20on%20returning.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ERollins%20is%20in%20the%20process%20of%20applying%20for%20French%20citizenship.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Amanda%20Rollins%2C%20an%20American%20from%20Massachuetts%20who%20moved%20to%20Paris%20six%20years%20ago.%20The%20conversation%20was%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20started%20learning%20French%20in%20sixth%20grade%20when%20I%20was%2012%2C%20and%20I%20loved%20it.%20I%20I%20kept%20studying%20French%20all%20through%20school%3A%20I%20was%20in%20AP%20French%20in%20high%20school%2C%20and%20president%20of%20the%20French%20club.%20And%20then%20when%20I%20went%20to%20college%2C%20I%20minored%20in%20French.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20just%20always%20wanted%20to%20visit%20Paris%2C%20but%20I%20grew%20up%20really%20low%20income%20and%20tickets%20are%20expensive.%20So%2C%20when%20I%20got%20my%20first%20big%20commission%20check%20from%20my%20sales%20job%2C%20the%20first%20thing%20I%20did%20was%20book%20a%20flight%20to%20Paris%20from%20my%20cell%20phone%20in%20a%20parking%20lot.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BI'm%20going%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20moment%20I%20saw%20the%20money%20hit%20my%20account.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20got%20back%2C%20I%20kept%20thinking%20to%20myself%2C%20if%20I%20could%20do%20anything%20I%20wanted%20I%20would%20live%20in%20Paris.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20kept%20making%20excuses%2C%20and%20then%20one%20day%2C%20I%20read%20the%20book%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Alchemist%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20second%20I%20did%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20make%20plans%20to%20move%20to%20Paris.%20So%20I%20made%20an%20account%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2FAuPairWorld.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAuPairWorld.com%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20a%20Monday%2C%20and%20by%20Friday%2C%20I%20found%20my%20family.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20signed%20the%20contract%2C%20I%20told%20my%20company%20that%20I%20was%20leaving%2C%20and%20then%20I%20made%20my%20appointment%20with%20the%20embassy%20to%20start%20the%20visa%20process.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20sold%20everything%20that%20I%20owned%20and%20moved%20here%20two%20months%20later%20with%20my%20cat%20and%20some%20clothes%2C%20and%20I%20have%20not%20looked%20back%20since.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ESix%20years%20later%2C%20I%20am%20planning%20to%20apply%20for%20citizenship%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EParis%20is%20the%20best%20city%20in%20the%20world.%20I%20love%20France%2C%20but%20Paris%2C%20especially%20every%20day%2C%20is%20like%20walking%20through%20a%20museum.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20buildings%20are%20art%2C%20everything%20is%20like%20a%20movie%2C%20everything%20is%20beautiful.%20Even%20the%20shittiest%20street%20seems%20like%20the%20most%20beautiful%20street%20I've%20seen%20in%20my%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20feel%20reborn%20here.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Amanda%20Rollins%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6503095d992da60019ec3fb8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAmanda%20Rollins%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Amanda%20Rollins%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20in%20the%20process%20right%20now%20of%20asking%20for%20citizenship.%20France%20is%20my%20home%20now%2C%20I%20just%20love%20it%20here%2C%20and%20I%20just%20wouldn't%20ever%20want%20to%20live%20in%20the%20US%20again.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFood%2C%20healthcare%2C%20and%20the%20quality%20of%20life%20are%20some%20reasons%20for%20that.%20The%20school%20shootings%2C%20and%20how%20polarized%20the%20country%20is%20are%20also%20reasons%20for%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20this%20is%20a%20perspective%20you%20can%20only%20have%20if%20you%20leave%20the%20US%2C%20you%20don't%20realize%20that%20you%20don't%20realize%20that%20there's%20a%20better%20way.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cbr%3E%3Cstrong%3EHealth%20is%20no%20longer%20an%20expense%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20remember%20one%20time%20in%20the%20US%2C%20I%20had%20to%20have%20this%20one%20surgery%2C%20or%C2%A0%20I%20had%20to%20have%20bloodwork.%20And%20I%20was%20like%2C%20can't%20do%20it.%20Can't%20afford%20it.%20That's%20crazy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20see%20these%20people%20who%20have%20a%20GoFundMe%20because%20their%20mom%20got%20cancer.%20It's%20like%20%26quot%3Byeah%2C%20they're%20going%20to%20have%20to%20get%20rid%20of%20the%20house.%26quot%3B%20That%20type%20of%20stuff%20really%20bothers%20me.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20have%20free%20healthcare%20here%2C%20so%20since%20I've%20moved%20here%2C%20my%20health%20is%20no%20longer%20a%20budget%20item%20for%20me.%20If%20I%20am%20sick%2C%20no%20problem.%20I%20went%20to%20the%20emergency%20room%20four%20times%20and%20I%20paid%20like%2016%20euros%20in%20total%2C%20then%20I%20was%20reimbursed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20take%20care%20of%20myself%20because%20I%20can%20%E2%80%94%20and%20that%20that%20alone%20is%20huge.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnyone%20that%20lives%20in%20France%2C%20permanently%20%E2%80%94%20even%20if%20it's%20just%20for%20school%20for%20one%20year%20%E2%80%94%20is%20entitled%20to%20the%20national%20healthcare%20system.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Amanda%20Rollins%20on%20a%20Seine%20Cruise%20in%20Paris%20eiffel%20tower%20in%20the%20background%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6503096c1afe8f0019ea58bf%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAmanda%20Rollins%20on%20a%20Seine%20Cruise%20in%20Paris%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Amanda%20Rollins%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20all%20I%20have%20right%20now%2C%20since%20I%20switched%20from%20my%20sales%20job%20to%20running%20my%20own%20business%20as%20a%20content%20creator.%20If%20I%20was%20working%20for%20a%20company%20I%20would%20have%20something%20called%20a%20%3Cem%3Emutuelle%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3Ewhich%20is%20supplemental.%20But%20I%20don't%20have%20it%20right%20now%2C%20because%20I%20don't%20even%20need%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20I%20go%20to%20the%20doctor%20right%20now%2C%20it's%2025%20euros%2C%20and%20then%20%3Cem%3Es%C3%A9curit%C3%A9%20sociale%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3Ethe%20social%20security%20program%20in%20France%20which%20covers%20healthcare%2C%20will%20reimburse%20me%20automatically.%20It's%20connected%20with%20my%20bank%20account%2C%20it'll%20reimburse%20me%20in%20three%20days.%20I%20think%20I%20get%20reimbursed%20most%2C%20if%20not%20all%20of%20it.%20At%20most%2C%20it's%20five%20bucks.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EFood%20and%20the%20pace%20of%20life%20are%20so%20much%20different%20than%20in%20the%20US%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20pace%20of%20life%20over%20here%20is%20so%20different.%20We%20take%20our%20time%2C%20we%20take%20long%20lunches%2C%20we%20have%20five%20weeks%20of%20vacation.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20entire%20month%20of%20August%2C%20everyone%20just%20goes%20to%20the%20south%20of%20France.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20I'm%20in%20the%20center%20of%20Europe%2C%20I%20can%20fly%20anywhere%20for%20so%20cheap.%20I%20flew%20to%20Barcelona%20for%2060%20euros%2C%20flew%20to%20Italy%20for%2060%20euros%2C%20and%20I%20went%20to%20the%20Canary%20Islands%20for%2091%20euros.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20of%20a%20sudden%20I%20have%20access%20to%20all%20these%20other%20countries%20that%20I%20never%20had%20before.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20food%20here%20alone%20is%20one%20reason%20I%20don't%20ever%20want%20to%20go%20back%20to%20the%20US.%20Do%20you%20know%20how%20many%20food%20ingredients%20are%20in%20American%20food%20that%20are%20banned%20in%20Europe%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ENatural%20beauty%20is%20valued%2C%20and%20everyone%20is%20very%20chic%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20don't%20wear%20makeup%20anymore%20because%20natural%20beauty%20is%20really%20encouraged.%20I%20love%20that%20because%20even%20if%20you%20care%20about%20these%20things%2C%20you%20can't%20help%20but%20be%20affected%20by%20the%20people%20around%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Amanda%20Rollins%20in%20Paris%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6503097a1afe8f0019ea58c4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAmanda%20Rollins%20in%20Paris.%20%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Amanda%20Rollins%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20I%20look%20around%20me%20and%20I%20see%20all%20the%20other%20women%20going%20bare-faced%20and%20I%20just%20think%20%26quot%3Bwe're%20all%20doing%20it.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrench%20people%20are%20chic%2C%20and%20%E2%80%94%20I'm%20not%20gonna%20lie%20to%20you%20%E2%80%94%20speaking%20French%20makes%20me%20feel%20so%20cool.%20I%20feel%20so%20cool%20that%20I'm%20fluent%20in%20French.%20That's%20my%20biggest%20flex%20in%20the%20entire%20world%20because%20it's%20not%20normal%20for%20Americans%20to%20speak%20two%20languages.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20cost%20of%20living%20is%20much%20less%20than%20in%20the%20US%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%