ted%20Russia's%20state-owned%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftass.ru%2Fmezhdunarodnaya-panorama%2F18720525%5C%22%3ETass%20news%20agency.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20co-founded%20the%20Gorki%20center%20and%20manage%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Tass%20quotes%20her%20as%20saying.%20%26quot%3BSince%20there%20is%20a%20lot%20of%20work%20there%20and%20it%20requires%20a%20lot%20of%20attention%2C%20I%20cannot%20do%20this%20in%20passing.%20I%20decided%20to%20move%20to%20St.%20Petersburg%20for%20this%20work.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKneissl%20was%20the%20foreign%20minister%20of%20Austria%20from%202017-2019%20and%20lost%20her%20position%20after%20a%20scandal%20engulfed%20the%20far-right%20Austrian%20Freedom%20Party%2C%20which%20appointed%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20then%20moved%20to%20France%20and%20then%20Lebanon%2C%20where%20she%20said%20she%20was%20living%20to%20%26quot%3Bsurvive%26quot%3B%20while%20commuting%20to%20Russia%20to%20work%2C%20per%C2%A0%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-66795596%5C%22%3EBBC%20News%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHer%20connections%20to%20Russia%20run%20deep%20%E2%80%94%20she%20was%20a%20regular%20contributor%20to%20the%20Russian%20state-backed%20news%20channel%20RT%2C%20widely%20viewed%20as%20the%20Kremlin's%20propaganda%20arm.%20She%20was%20also%20once%20a%20board%20member%20of%20the%20state-owned%20oil%20company%20Rosneft.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKneissl%20said%20on%20social%20media%20that%20she%20took%20a%20Russian%20military%20plane%20to%20St.%20Petersburg%20along%20with%20her%20possessions%20%E2%80%94%20and%20ponies%20%E2%80%94%20as%20due%20to%20sanctions%20against%20Syria%20there%20were%20no%20commercial%20flights%20or%20DHL.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%2C%20therefore%2C%20had%20the%20option%20of%20accompanying%20a%20Russian%20transport%20flight%20from%20Syria%20to%20Russia%2C%20for%20which%20I%20am%20very%20grateful%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20wrote%20in%20a%20Telegram%20post%2C%20per%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%