Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20believe%20that%20this%20phenomenon%20is%20the%20only%20one%20that%20gives%20us%20the%20opportunity%20to%20unite%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EElsa%20Tomasto-Cagigao%2C%20a%20respected%20Peruvian%20bio-anthropologist%2C%20is%20frustrated%20such%20claims%20are%20still%20being%20given%20publicity%2C%20citing%20similar%20alleged%20finds%20that%20were%20found%20to%20be%20frauds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20we%20said%20before%20still%20stands%2C%20they%20are%20presenting%20the%20same%20rehash%20as%20always%20and%20if%20there%20are%20people%20that%20keep%20believing%20that%2C%20what%20can%20we%20do%3F%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20by%20phone.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20so%20crass%20and%20so%20simple%20that%20there%20is%20nothing%20more%20to%20add.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPrevious%20such%20finds%20have%20been%20dismissed%20by%20the%20scientific%20community%20as%20mutilated%20mummies%20of%20pre-Hispanic%20children%2C%20sometimes%20combined%20with%20bits%20of%20animal%20parts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ENASA%20wants%20more%20information%20on%20'1%2C000-Year-Old%20alien%20bodies'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDavid%20Spergel%2C%20former%20head%20of%20Princeton%20University's%20astrophysics%20department%20and%20chair%20of%20a%20NASA%20report%20into%20unidentified%20anomalous%20phenomena%2C%20said%20on%20Thursday%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwhen-you-have-what-nasa-said-about-alien-bodies-in-mexico-4391401%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esuch%20samples%20should%20be%20made%20available%20for%20testing%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20the%20world's%20scientific%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMaussan%20shared%20on%20social%20media%20and%20in%20his%20presentation%20the%20results%20of%20DNA%20and%20carbon%20dating%20tests%20that%20he%20said%20he%20commissioned%20on%20%26quot%3Bthe%20beings.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Mexican%20scientist%2C%20at%20the%20request%20of%20Reuters%2C%20reviewed%20the%20results%20an