2%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fasia-cup-2023%2Fan-age-old-problem-shahid-afridi-lashes-out-at-pakistan-management-after-asia-cup-elimination-4394812%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fasia-cup-2023%2Fan-age-old-problem-shahid-afridi-lashes-out-at-pakistan-management-after-asia-cup-elimination-4394812%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fasia-cup-2023%2Fan-age-old-problem-shahid-afridi-lashes-out-at-pakistan-management-after-asia-cup-elimination-4394812%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BWe're%20All%20Sinners%26quot%3B%3A%20Women%20Supporters%20Stand%20By%20Trump%20Despite%20'Sexcapades'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFormer%20US%20president%20Donald%20Trump%20courted%20evangelical%20Christians%20and%20women%20at%20two%20back-to-back%20Washington%20events%20on%20Friday%20--%20voting%20blocks%20whose%20loyalties%20to%20him%20once%20seemed%20contradictory%20but%20have%20now%20become%20a%20well-established%20part%20of%20his%20base.%20The%20legal%2C%20moral%20and%20sexual%20escapades%20of%20the%20scandal-plagued%20frontrunner%20for%20the%202024%20Republican%20presidential%20nomination%20have%20earned%20him%20indictments%2C%20impeachments%20and%20public%20scorn%20in%20many%20quarters.%C2%A0But%20support%20among%20his%20devotees%20remains%20strong.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20a%20woman%20I%20understand%20that%20he%20can%20be%20offensive%2C%26quot%3B%20Joan%20Horswell%2C%20a%2076-year-old%20retired%20nurse%20from%20Texas%2C%20told%20AFP.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20%26quot%3Bpersonally%2C%20I%20like%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20at%20the%20%26quot%3BPray%20Vote%20Stand%26quot%3B%20summit%2C%20put%20on%20by%20the%20conservative%20Christian%20group%20Family%20Research%20Council.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESomething%20of%20a%20rock%20star%20among%20white%20evangelical%20Protestants%2C%2084%20percent%20of%20whom%20voted%20for%20him%20in%202020%2C%20Trump%20also%20holds%20his%20own%20among%20women%2C%20having%20won%2044%20percent%20of%20their%20vote%20in%20the%20last%20election%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Pew%20Research%20Center.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20election%20will%20decide%20whether%20America%20will%20be%20ruled%20by%20Marxist%2C%20fascist%2C%20communist%20tyrants%20who%20want%20to%20smash%20the%20Judeo-Christian%20heritage%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%2C%2077%2C%20said%20at%20the%20summit%2C%20%26quot%3Bor%20whether%20America%20will%20be%20saved%20by%20God-fearing%20freedom-loving%20patriots%20like%20all%20of%20the%20people%20in%20this%20room.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIs%20he%20a%20flawed%20individual%3F%20Sure.%20But%20most%20Christians%20will%20say%2C%20we%20are%20all%20sinners.%20Jesus%20is%20not%20on%20the%20ballot%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20William%20Wan%2C%20a%2060-year-old%20Catholic%20engineer%20from%20Winter%20Garden%2C%20Florida%20who%20attended%20the%20summit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20Trump%20may%20strike%20many%20as%20offensive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20found%20liable%20in%20a%20civil%20trial%20in%20May%20for%20sexually%20abusing%20writer%20E.%20Jean%20Carroll%20in%201996.%20He's%20also%20set%20to%20go%20on%20trial%20for%20allegedly%20paying%20election-eve%20hush%20money%20to%20a%20porn%20star.%20And%20he%20was%20heard%20boasting%20of%20groping%20women%20when%20the%20infamous%20%26quot%3BAccess%20Hollywood%26quot%3B%20tape%20was%20published.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20lots%20of%20conservative%20evangelicals%20believe%20he%20%26quot%3Bis%20the%20perfect%20man%20for%20the%20job%20precisely%20because%20he%20does%20not%20reflect%20Christian%20values%2C%26quot%3B%20Kristin%20Du%20Mez%2C%20a%20history%20professor%20at%20Calvin%20University%2C%20told%20AFP.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump's%20supporters%20%26quot%3Bcertainly%20like%20what%20he's%20done%20for%20them.%20But%20I%20think%20that%20many%20are%20also%20very%20comfortable%20with%20how%20he's%20done%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Du%20Mez%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20points%20to%20his%20take-no-prisoners%20approach%20in%20getting%20conservative%20Christians%20what%20they%20wanted%2C%20from%20ending%20the%20federal%20right%20to%20an%20abortion%20to%20recognizing%20Jerusalem%20as%20Israel's%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHer%20book%20%26quot%3BJesus%20and%20John%20Wayne%26quot%3B%20chronicles%20the%20rise%20of%20rugged%20masculinity%20ideology%20within%20white%20evangelical%20Christianity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPenny%20Nance%2C%20CEO%20of%20conservative%20Christian%20women's%20group%20Concerned%20Women%20for%20America%2C%20echoed%20this%20dogma%20when%20she%20introduced%20Trump%20before%20he%20spoke%20across%20town%20at%20a%20leadership%20summit%20for%20her%20advocacy%20group%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BConservative%20women%20are%20not%20looking%20for%20a%20pastor%20or%20a%20husband%20for%20president%2C%20we%20are%20looking%20for%20a%20bodyguard%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20the%20audience%20to%20cheers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSomeone%20willing%20to%20stick%20the%20knife%20in%20his%20teeth%20and%20swim%20the%20moat%20to%20our%20rescue%20from%20those%20who%20threaten%20our%20safety%20and%20our%20freedom.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMelissa%20Deckman%2C%20CEO%20of%20the%20nonpartisan%20Public%20Religion%20Research%20Institute%2C%20points%20out%20that%20while%20some%20political%20observers%20had%20initially%20been%20surprised%20by%20the%20number%20of%20women%20willing%20to%20vote%20for%20Trump%2C%20not%20all%20women%20see%20eye-to-eye%20on%20issues%20of%20sex%20and%20sexism.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAmerican%20women%20are%20far%20from%20monolithic%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20attitudes%20about%20gender%20dynamics%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20AFP%20in%20an%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump's%20former%20vice%20president%20Mike%20Pence%20--%20who%20is%20also%20running%20for%20the%20Republican%202024%20nomination%20and%20spoke%20at%20the%20%26quot%3BPray%20Vote%20Stand%26quot%3B%20summit%20--%20brandishes%20authentic%20evangelical%20bone%20fides%20as%20a%20deeply%20religious%20long-time%20churchgoer%20who%20has%20described%20himself%20as%20%26quot%3Ba%20Christian%2C%20a%20conservative%2C%20and%20a%20Republican%2C%20in%20that%20order.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYet%20only%20five%20percent%20of%20surveyed%20white%2C%20evangelical%20potential%20Republican%20primary%20voters%20said%20they%20would%20choose%20him%20as%20their%20nominee.%20Trump%20meanwhile%20would%20receive%2056%20percent%20of%20their%20vote%2C%20according%20to%20a%20July%202023%20New%20York%20Times%2FSiena%20Poll.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20is%20the%20clearest%20kind%20of%20white%20evangelical%20poster%20boy%20out%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Du%20Mez.%20%26quot%3BThey%20might%20want%20(Pence)%20as%20a%20Sunday%20school%20teacher%3B%20that's%20not%20who%20they%20want%20in%20the%20Oval%20Office.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHorswell%2C%20the%20retired%20nurse%2C%20thinks%20%26quot%3BMike%20Pence%20is%20OK%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20adds%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20at%20this%20point%20in%20our%20government%2C%20we%20need%20a%20much%20stronger%20man.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20conservative%20Christians%2C%20Trump's%20accomplishments%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bstrong%20man%26quot%3B%20are%20many.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20appointed%20three%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court's%20nine%20justices%2C%20creating%20a%20bench%20that%20went%20on%20to%20overturn%20abortion%20rights.%20In%202020%20he%20became%20the%20first%20sitting%20president%20to%20attend%20the%20annual%20anti-abortion%20March%20for%20Life%20rally%20in%20Washington.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20he%20has%20repeatedly%20expressed%20his%20opinion%20that%20gender%20is%20biological%2C%20siding%20against%20trans%20inclusion%20in%20women's%20sports%20and%20against%20gender-affirming%20care%20for%20minors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAny%20personality%20flaws%20take%20a%20back%20seat%20said%20Deckman%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20moral%20character%2C%20I%20think%2C%20matters%20less%20in%20some%20ways%20than%20what%20a%20candidate%20is%20willing%20to%20stand%20for%20and%20fight%20for.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20Wan%2C%20the%20engineer%20from%20Florida%2C%20put%20it%2C%20%26quot%3Bmany%20Christians%20would%20argue%20we're%20electing%20a%20president%2C%20we%20are%20not%20electing%20a%20chief%20theologian.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694853060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fhjv4ufj8_donald-trump-afp_650x400_25_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdonald-trump-us-president-elections-republicans-we-are-all-sinners-women-supporters-stand-by-trump-despite-sexcapades-4395205%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Former%20US%20president%20Donald%20Trump%20courted%20evangelical%20Christians%20and%20women%20at%20two%20back-to-back%20Washington%20events%20on%20Friday%20--%20voting%20blocks%20whose%20loyalties%20to%20him%20once%20seemed%20contradictory%20but%20have%20now%20become%20a%20well-established%20part%20of%20his%20base.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdonald-trump-us-president-elections-republicans-we-are-all-sinners-women-supporters-stand-by-trump-despite-sexcapades-4395205%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22What%20to%20watch%20on%20OTT%20this%20week%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694853000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-103683948%2Cimgsize-48838.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fweb-series%2Fnews%2Fhindi%2Fbarbie-rocky-aur-rani-kii-prem-kahaani-and-others-what-to-watch-on-ott-this-week%2Farticleshow%2F103683967.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5