0cricket%20captain%2C%20the%20legendary%20Arjuna%20Ranatunga%2C%20has%20hit%20out%20at%20%E2%80%9Cone%20board%20or%20one%20individual%E2%80%9D%20%5Breferring%20to%20the%20BCCI%5D%20making%20arbitrary%20decisions%20and%20said%20that%20the%20Asian%20Cricket%20Council%20(ACC)%20and%20International%20Cricket%20Council%20(ICC)%20need%20to%20stand%20up%20and%20be%20counted.%20Jay%20Shah%2C%20BCCI%20secretary%2C%20is%20also%20the%20president%20of%20the%20ACC.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECriticising%20the%20decision%20to%20add%C2%A0a%20reserve%20day%C2%A0for%20the%20Asia%20Cup%20Super-Four%20match%20between%20India%20and%20Pakistan%2C%20which%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.espncricinfo.com%2Fstory%2Freserve-day-for-pakistan-vs-india-game-you-are-looking-at-a-disaster-says-arjuna-ranatunga-1398547%5C%22%3EESPN%20Cricinfo%20noted%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20was%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20only%20game%20in%20the%20tournament%20apart%20from%20the%20final%20to%20get%20the%20advantage%20%E2%80%93%20after%20the%20tournament%20had%20started%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20portal%20reported%20that%20%E2%80%9CArjuna%20Ranatunga%20has%20warned%20that%20favouring%20one%20team%20(read%20India)%20over%20others%20will%20put%20international%20cricket%20in%20peril.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CYou%20take%20the%20Asia%20Cup.%20You%20have%20rules%20before%20the%20tournament%2C%20but%20before%20that%20one%20game%2C%20they%20changed%20the%20rules%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ranatunga%20was%20quoted%20by%20PTI%20as%20saying%20at%20an%20interaction%20with%20members%20of%20the%20media.%20%E2%80%9CWhere%20is%20ACC%3F%20Where%20is%20ICC%3F%20I%20am%20not%20very%20comfortable%20when%20you%20have%20a%20tournament%20where%20you%20change%20rules%20for%20one%20team.%20You%20are%20looking%20at%20a%20disaster%20in%20the%20future.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20didn%E2%80%99t%20stop%20at%20that.%20%E2%80%9CI%20won%E2%80%99t%20be%20surprised%20if%20they%20change%20the%20rule%20before%20the%20India-Pakistan%20game%20%5Bat%20the%20upcoming%20ODI%20World%20Cup%5D%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ranatunga%20said.%20%E2%80%9CICC%20will%20keep%20their%20mouth%20shut%20and%20say%20%E2%80%98okay%2C%20do%20it%E2%80%99.%20ICC%20just%20talks%20rubbish%2C%20nothing%20happens.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERanatunga%20said%20world%20cricket%20should%20not%20be%20governed%20by%20one%20board%20or%20one%20individual%2C%20and%20that%20other%20boards%20should%20stand%20up%20for%20their%20rights%2C%20reported%20ESPN%20Cricinfo.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20had%20sharp%20things%20to%20say%20on%20%E2%80%9Cformer%20cricketers%E2%80%9D%20who%20need%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20bucks%E2%80%9D%20that%20BCCI%20has%20to%20offer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20feel%20very%20sad%20for%20ICC%20and%20ACC%20because%20they%20just%20want%20to%20hold%20the%20positions.%20Former%20cricketers%20too%20don%E2%80%99t%20open%2C%20simply%20because%20they%20need%20the%20bucks%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20is%20reported%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Asian%20Cricket%20Council%E2%80%99s%20(ACC)%20decision%20to%20keep%20a%20reserve%20day%20only%20for%20the%C2%A0India%20vs%20Pakistan%20match%C2%A0in%20the%20Asia%20Cup%202023%20(other%20than%20the%20tournament%20final)%20received%20a%20lot%20of%20flak.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fcricket%2Fbcci-is-powerful-or-one-person-ranatunga-lambasts-unprofessional-icc-tears-acc-for-ind-vs-pak-reserve-day-101694834472299.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20decision%20%5Bto%20have%20a%20Reserve%20Day%5D%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20a%20crucial%20one%20as%20India%20won%20the%20match%20by%20a%20record%20margin%20on%20the%20reserve%20on%20the%20reserve%20day.%20If%20it%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20for%20a%20mid-tournament%20rule%20change%20then%20India%20and%20Pakistan%20would%20have%20shared%20points%20for%20that%20match%20and%20because%20India%20lost%20their%20last%20Super%204%20match%20to%20Bangladesh%2C%20they%20would%20have%20been%20knocked%20out%20of%20the%20tournament%20instead%20of%20Pakistan.%20Of%20course%2C%20these%20are%20all%20hypothetical%20scenarios%20but%20that%E2%80%99s%20how%20significant%20the%20reserve%20day%20was.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBCCI%20has%20as%20its%20secretary%2C%20Jay%20Shah%2C%20also%20the%20son%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20effectively%20considered%20the%20only%20other%20power%20centre%20that%20matters%20after%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20in%20India.%20Shah%20became%20secretary%20at%20the%20age%20of%2030%2C%20raising%20eyebrows%20at%20the%20time.%20BCCI%20and%20Shah%E2%80%99s%20alleged%20hold%20over%20the%20international%20cricket%20calendar%20has%20come%20under%20a%20cloud%20after%20a%20recent%20investigation.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcaravanmagazine.in%2Fsports%2Fbjp-bcci-jay-shah%5C%22%3ESharda%20Ugra%20wrote%20in%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Caravan%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20the%20BCCI%E2%80%99s%20arrogance%20has%20been%20moored%20around%20money%2C%20it%20has%20also%20benefited%20from%20cross-party%20political%20connections%20%E2%80%93%20the%20organisation%20has%20usually%20featured%20politicians%20from%20both%20sides%20of%20the%20aisle.%20What%20is%20now%20at%20play%2C%20however%2C%20is%20something%20different.%20In%20what%20already%20was%20a%20monopsony%2C%20an%20oligarch%20has%20taken%20over%20the%20cartel.%20We%20are%20witnessing%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20the%20BCCI%20the%20gradual%20solidification%20of%20the%20soft%20power%20of%20not%20politicians%20as%20a%20lot%20but%20of%20a%20single%20political%20party.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Freserve-day-added-for-india-pakistan-cricket-match-mid-tournament-triggers-controversy%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20had%20reported%20earlier%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20how%20India-Pakistan%20tensions%20and%20the%20control%20that%20BCCI%20has%20on%20international%20cricket%20bodies%20was%20being%20noticed%20and%20coming%20under%20scrutiny.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%2