ompass%20more%20affordable%20by%2020%25%20(almost%206%20lakhs)!%20The%20company%20has%20also%20unveiled%20the%20new%20Jeep%20Meridian%20Overland%20Edition%20SUV%20with%20updated%20features.%20It%20is%20powered%20by%20a%202.0-litre%20turbocharged%20engine%20mated%20to%20a%20nine-speed%20automatic%20transmission.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22PRACHI%20AHLUWALIA%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fauto%2Fcars%2F2023-jeep-compass-4x2-launched-prices-lower-by-nearly-rs-six-lakh%2Farticleshow%2F103709882.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Analysis%3A%20The%20Politics%20That%20Keeps%20Cauvery%20Water%20Dispute%20On%20The%20Boil%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAll%20those%20years%20when%20the%20monsoon%20fails%20to%20fill%20the%20reservoirs%20in%20Karnataka%20it%20has%20wide%20ramifications%20for%20the%20people%20of%20the%20state%20and%20those%20living%20in%20the%20Cauvery%20delta%20basin%20in%20adjoining%20Tamil%20Nadu.%20On%20September%2013%2C%20Karnataka%20informed%20the%20centre%20that%20the%20decision%20of%20the%20Cauvery%20Water%20Regulation%20Committee%20(CWRC)%2C%20asking%20the%20state%20to%20release%20water%20at%20the%20rate%20of%205%2C000%20cusecs%20daily%2C%20cannot%20be%20practically%20implemented.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChief%20Minister%20Siddaramaiah%20wrote%20a%20letter%20to%20the%20Union%20Jal%20Shakti%20Minister%20reiterating%20that%20the%20state%20can't%20release%20water%20without%20endangering%20the%20interest%20of%20farmers%20for%20irrigation%20and%20sustenance%20of%20humans%20and%20livestock%20dependent%20on%20the%20Cauvery%20for%20drinking%20water.%20The%20latest%20controversy%20over%20Cauvery%20water%20sharing%20erupted%20after%20the%20CWRC%20on%20September%2012%20ordered%20Karnataka%20to%20release%205%2C000%20cusecs%20of%20water%20to%20Tamil%20Nadu%20for%2015%20more%20days%20starting%20September%2013%2C%20against%20the%20demand%20for%2012%2C500%20cusecs%20of%20water%20by%20Tamil%20Nadu's%20DMK%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20government%20had%20approached%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20requesting%20it%20to%20direct%20Karnataka%20to%20release%2024%2C000%20cusecs%20of%20water%20daily%20from%20its%20reservoirs.%20Karnataka%20too%20filed%20an%20affidavit%20opposing%20Tamil%20Nadu's%20plea%20stating%20that%20their%20assumption%20is%20based%20on%20normal%20rain%20this%20year%2C%20which%20is%20not%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BKarnataka%20repeatedly%20says%20Tamil%20Nadu%20gets%20north-east%20monsoon%2C%20and%20has%20groundwater.%20All%20these%20are%20not%20at%20all%20relevant%20for%20the%20purpose%20of%20deciding%2C%20because%20the%20obligation%20of%20Karnataka%20is%20to%20release%20177%20tnc%20(thousand%20million%20cubic%20feet)%20during%20the%20normal%20water%20year.%20Going%20by%20any%20yardstick%2C%20we%20have%20not%20got%20our%20stipulated%20water%20during%20the%20current%20year%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20G%20Umapathy%2C%20Senior%20Advocate%2C%20representing%20Tamil%20Nadu.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2018-12%2Ftcmf0pfo_cauvery_625x300_29_December_18.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20Cauvery%20Water%20Dispute%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20river%20Cauvery%20is%20a%20major%20source%20of%20sustenance%20and%20livelihood%20for%20the%20people%20of%20both%20states%20helping%20them%20meet%20their%20drinking%20water%20and%20irrigation%20needs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20centre%20formed%20the%20Cauvery%20Water%20Disputes%20Tribunal%20(CWDT)%20on%20June%202%2C%201990%20to%20adjudicate%20on%20the%20disputes%20between%20Karnataka%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%20and%20Puducherry%20with%20respect%20to%20their%20water-sharing%20capacities.%20The%20CWDT's%20concluding%20judgment%20of%20February%202007%20allotted%2030%20tmc%20of%20water%20to%20Kerala%2C%20270%20tmc%20to%20Karnataka%2C%20419%20tmc%20to%20Tamil%20Nadu%20and%207%20tmc%20to%20Puducherry.%20The%20plan%20was%20notified%20by%20the%20centre%20in%202013%20on%20the%20direction%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20then%20Congress-led%20government%20didn't%20abide%20by%20the%20tribunal's%20decision.%20In%20March%202013%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%20approached%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20seeking%20directions%20to%20the%20Water%20Ministry%20for%20setting%20up%20a%20Cauvery%20Management%20Board%20(CMB).%20Tamil%20Nadu%20again%20moved%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20in%20May%202013%20seeking%20Rs%202%2C480%20crore%20in%20damages%20from%20Karnataka%20for%20not%20following%20the%20orders%20of%20the%20CWDT.%20The%20year%20it%20doesn't%20rain%20copiously%2C%20the%20dispute%20flared%20up%20over%20water%20as%20Karnataka%2C%20the%20upstream%20state%2C%20citing%20less-than-normal%20rain%20stops%20sharing%20water%20with%20its%20co-riparian%20Tamil%20Nadu.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BKarnataka%20in%20normal%20water%20year%20must%20ensure%20177.25%20tmc%20of%20flow%20annually%20at%20the%20inter-state%20border%20-%20Biligundlu%3B%20during%20the%20surplus%20year%2C%20the%20surplus%20generated%20in%20Karnataka%20goes%20for%20Karnataka's%20benefit%3B%20and%20during%20the%20distressed%20year%2C%20the%20distress%20must%20be%20shared%20in%20a%20proportionate%20or%20pro%20rata%20basis.%20At%20present%2C%20disputes%20have%20arisen%20on%20the%20sharing%20of%20distress%20since%20the%20south-west%20monsoon%20in%20this%20water%20year%20has%20failed%20in%20Karnataka%20and%20north-east%20monsoon%2C%20which%20benefits%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20has%20not%20begun%20yet%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Mohan%20V%20Katarki%2C%20senior%20advocate%20representing%20Karnataka.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2018-12%2Fbtcl08ro_cauvery_625x300_28_December_18.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20proportionate%20sharing%20of%20distress%20is%20easier%20said%20than%20done.%20There%20is%20no%20formula.%20Karnataka%20wants%20equitable%20solutions%20based%20on%20ground%20realities%20and%20assessment%20of%20needs%20as%20assessed%20by%20the%20statutory%20body%20namely%20Cauvery%20Water%20Management%20Authority.%20But%20Tamil%20Nadu%20has%20a%20different%20formula%20of%20taking%20only%20the%20shortfall%20in%20Karnataka's%20reservoirs%20as%20yardstick%20without%20accounting%20for%20the%20resources%20in%20its%20territory%20and%20in%20the%20territory%20between%20Karnataka's%20reservoirs%20and%20border%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Mr%20Katarki.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETamil%20Nadu's%20counsel%20had%20a%20different%20take.%20%26quot%3BKarnataka%20has%20been%20crying%20that%20we%20irrigate%20more.%20In%20fact%2C%20we%20have%20only%20planted%205%20lakh%20acres.%20Even%20that%20is%20going%20to%20suffer%20for%20want%20of%20water.%20Out%20of%20five%2C%20two%20lakh%20acres%20is%20'Kuruvai'%20or%20short-term%20crop%20and%20the%20balance%20is%20'Samba'%20or%20long-term%20crop.%20If%20Karnataka%20doesn't%20release%20water%20for%2010-15%20days%2C%20the%20paddy%20will%20wither%20away.%20The%20north-east%20monsoon%20is%20always%20erratic%20and%20undependable.%20%C2%A0Sometimes%20we%20get%20good%20rain%20and%20sometimes%20we%20get%20floods.%20Floods%20will%20further%20destroy%20the%20crops%2C%26quot%3B%20adds%20Mr%20Umapathy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBesides%20the%20courts%2C%20the%20battle%20for%20water%20has%20been%20on%20at%20the%20ground%20level%20as%20well%20without%20any%20solution%20in%20sight.%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20effectiveness%20of%20the%20CWRC%20and%20CMB%20has%20been%20questioned%2C%20with%20the%20impacted%20party%20claiming%20bias.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPolitics%20Over%20Cauvery%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20suited%20politicians%20of%20both%20the%20states%20to%20make%20it%20an%20emotional%20issue%20and%20reap%20electoral%20benefits%20from%20it%20than%20to%20solve%20the%20problem%20logically%20in%20the%20interest%20of%20the%20people.%20Political%20parties%20in%20both%20the%20states%20-%20AIADMK%20and%20DMK%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%3B%20and%20Congress%2C%20BJP%20and%20JD(S)%20in%20Karnataka%20-%20who%20have%20been%20in%20power%20at%20one%20time%20or%20the%20other%20have%20not%20made%20any%20attempt%20to%20amicably%20solve%20the%20issue%20in%20the%20interest%20of%20the%20people.%20On%20the%20contrary%2C%20in%20the%20guise%20of%20protecting%20the%20interests%20of%20their%20respective%20state%2C%20politicians%20have%20fanned%20violence%20and%20unrest%2C%20in%20which%20many%20innocent%20lives%20have%20been%20lost.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2018-02%2Fcauvery_650x400_61518771955.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20traditional%20rivalry%20between%20the%20states%20needs%20to%20be%20seen%20in%20a%20new%20light%20after%20the%20formation%20of%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20where%20both%20warring%20parties%20in%20government%20-%20Congress%20in%20Karnataka%20and%20DMK%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20-%20will%20fight%20elections%20under%20the%20same%20banner%20in%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%20This%20has%20given%20their%20rivals%20a%20chance%20to%20accuse%20them%20of%20compromising%20their%20state%20and%20people's%20interest%20for%20their%20parochial%20electoral%20benefits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Opposition%20BJP%20and%20JD(S)%20leaders%20in%20Karnataka%20have%20alleged%20that%20the%20CWRC%20order%20will%20push%20Karnataka%20farmers%20into%20a%20debt%20trap.%20Earlier%2C%20Union%20Minister%20and%20BJP%20leader%20Rajeev%20Chandrasekhar%20charged%20Mr%20Siddaramaiah%20and%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20DK%20Shivakumar%20of%20acting%20under%20pressure%20from%20the%20%26quot%3Barrogant%20DMK%26quot%3B%20and%20releasing%20Cauvery%20water%20without%20consulting%20the%20court%20and%20other%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20Tamil%20Maanila%20Congress%20claimed%20that%20the%20state%20lacked%20a%20bold%20Chief%20Minister%3A%20%26quot%3BHow%20can%20people%20vote%20for%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20here%20when%20the%20Congress%20government%20in%20Karnataka%20is%20not%20releasing%20water%20for%20Tamil%20Nadu%3F%26quot%3B.%20Both%20DMK%20and%20Congress%20are%20allies%20in%20the%20opposition%20bloc%20INDIA.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-09%2Fm8qt98pg_cauvery-basin_625x300_29_September_19.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EKarnataka%20has%20been%20batting%20for%20the%20Mekedatu%20multi-purpose%20project%20(for%20irrigation%20and%20power)%20within%20its%20territory.%20However%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%20feels%20it%20is%20just%20a%20ploy%20to%20divert%20water%20flow%20to%20the%20state.%20%26quot%3BAn%20outstanding%20solution%20to%20the%20distress%20is%20the%20construction%20of%20Mekedatu%20Reservoir%20at%20the%20border%20by%20Karnataka%20which%20will%20help%20in%20generating%20electricity%2C%20meeting%20Bangalore's%20drinking%20water%20supply%20and%20in%20helping%20Tamil%20Nadu%20to%20the%20extent%20of%2013%20tmc%20during%20a%20distress%20year.%20Unfortunately%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%20is%20objecting%20to%20this%20win-win%20solution%2C%26quot%3B%20adds%20lawyer%20Katarki.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKarnataka%20and%20Tamil%20Nadu%20have%20been%20embroiled%20in%20a%20prolonged%20dispute%2C%20but%20a%20resolution%20remains%20elusive.%20In%20a%20world%20where%20international%20disputes%20are%20resolved%20amicably%2C%20it's%20hard%20to%20believe%20and%20rationalise%20that%20there%20is%20no%20attempt%20to%20resolve%20the%20Cauvery%20dispute%