d%20she%20met%20the%20teenager%2C%20and%20that%20he%20was%20hardly%20able%20to%20lift%20his%20head%20from%20his%20chest.%20She%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20has%20sent%20shockwaves%20through%20the%20community%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20councillor%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20Indo-Canadian%20community%20is%20shocked%20by%20this%20...%20this%20is%20absolutely%20despicable.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20the%20second%20attack%20on%20a%20Sikh%20student%20in%20the%20central%20Interior%20city%20this%20year.%20On%20March%2017%2C%20another%20Indian%20Sikh%20student%20Gagandeep%20Singh%20was%20also%20attacked%2C%20according%20to%20CBC%20News%20report.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20Royal%20Canadian%20Mounted%20Police%20said%20investigators%20were%20carrying%20out%20consultations%20with%20their%20hate%20crimes%20unit.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694847900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2020-11%2Fk9fsv1r8_canada-policeafp_625x300_02_November_20.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Findia-strongly-condemns-assault-on-sikh-student-in-canada-calls-for-prompt-action-4394761%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Consulate%20General%20of%20India%20in%20Vancouver%20has%20strongly%20condemned%20the%20assault%20on%20a%20Sikh%20student%20in%20Canada's%20British%20Columbia%20province%20and%20called%20for%20prompt%20action%20against%20perpetrators.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Findia-strongly-condemns-assault-on-sikh-student-in-canada-calls-for-prompt-action-4394761%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Even%20After%20Monu%20Manesar's%20Arrest%2C%20Junaid%20and%20Nasir's%20Kin%20Continue%20to%20Face%20Hardships%2C%20Live%20in%20Fear%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F16122609%2Fimage-1318.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstro