story%2Famp%2Fsir-keir-starmer-to-warn-west-faces-axis-of-instability-as-he-appears-at-canada-summit-12962305%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fsir-keir-starmer-to-warn-west-faces-axis-of-instability-as-he-appears-at-canada-summit-12962305%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22South%20Korean%20Woman%20Found%20Guilty%20Of%20Stalking%20Daughter%2C%20Jailed%20For%206%20Months%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20woman%20in%20South%20Korea%20has%20been%20sentenced%20to%20six%20months%20in%20jail%20and%20two%20years%20of%20probation%20after%20she%20was%20found%20guilty%20of%20stalking%20and%20harassing%20her%20adult%20daughter%2C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.independent.co.uk%2Fasia%2Feast-asia%2Fmom-stalking-daughter-jailed-south-korea-b2412041.html%5C%22%3E%C2%A0the%20%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3EIndependent%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3Ereported.%20While%20her%20name%20has%20not%20been%20revealed%2C%20she%20is%20said%20to%20be%20in%20her%2050s.%20The%20harassment%2C%20which%20occurred%20from%20December%202021%20to%20May%202022%2C%20involved%20306%20text%20messages%20and%20111%20phone%20calls%2C%20according%20to%20Daejeon%20District%20Court%20documents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20initial%20messages%20were%20normal%20and%20mostly%20contained%20ordinary%20requests%20like%C2%A0suggesting%20Bible%20readings%20or%20asking%20about%20whereabouts.%20However%2C%20when%20she%20did%20not%20receive%20replies%20from%20her%20daughter%20for%20a%20long%20period%20of%20time%2C%20the%20messages%20became%20abusive%2C%C2%A0including%20derogatory%20comments%20about%20the%20daughter's%20sexual%20behaviour.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20only%20that%2C%20the%20woman%20then%20resorted%20to%C2%A0physically%20stalking%20her%20daughter%20and%20dropping%20her%20at%20her%20residence%20multiple%20times%2C%20unannounced.%20She%20also%20used%20to%C2%A0peep%20into%20her%20daughter's%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20data-t%3D%5C%22%7B%26quot%3Bn%26quot%3B%3A%26quot%3BblueLinks%26quot%3B%7D%5C%22%3EDespite%20a%20police%20injunction%20issued%20last%20June%2C%20the%20woman%20trespassed%20six%20more%20times.%C2%A0She%20claimed%20that%20her%20actions%20were%20not%20deliberate%2C%20but%20the%20court%20dismissed%20her%20argument.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20data-t%3D%5C%22%7B%26quot%3Bn%26quot%3B%3A%26quot%3BblueLinks%26quot%3B%7D%5C%22%3EThe%20court%20then%20handed%20her%20a%20prison%20sentence%20of%20six%20months%20and%20also%20ordered%20her%20to%20complete%2040%20hours%20of%20anti-stalking%20education.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20data-t%3D%5C%22%7B%26quot%3Bn%26quot%3B%3A%26quot%3BblueLinks%26quot%3B%7D%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20South%20Korean%20law%2C%20individuals%20found%20guilty%20of%20stalking%20can%20face%20fines%20of%20up%20to%2030%20million%20won%20(Rs%2018%2C78%2C008)%20or%20imprisonment%20for%20a%20maximum%20of%20three%20years.%C2%A0In%20March%202021%2C%20lawmakers%20in%20the%20country%20passed%20a%20stricter%20law%20against%20stalkers%20which%20went%20into%20effect%20in%20October%202021%2C%20as%20per%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.straitstimes.com%2Fasia%2Feast-asia%2Fmom-in-south-korea-found-guilty-of-stalking-daughter-sentenced-to-6-months-jail%5C%22%3EStraits%20Times.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20data-t%3D%5C%22%7B%26quot%3Bn%26quot%3B%3A%26quot%3BblueLinks%26quot%3B%7D%5C%22%3EIn%20cases%20where%20the%20offender%20stalks%20while%20carrying%20a%20weapon%2C%20the%20penalty%20increases%20to%2050%20million%20won%20(31%2C25%2C083)%20and%20a%20five-year%20jail%20sentence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20data-t%3D%5C%22%7B%26quot%3Bn%26quot%3B%3A%26quot%3BblueLinks%26quot%3B%7D%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694846220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2F8f2ni018_jail-cell_625x300_16_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fsouth-korean-mother-found-guilty-of-stalking-own-daughter-gets-6-months-in-jail-4394997%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20court%20then%20handed%20her%20a