-rajas-idol-unveiled-check-here-4394826%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fmumbai-news%2Fganesh-chaturthi-festival-2023-first-look-of-mumbais-lalbaugcha-rajas-idol-unveiled-check-here-4394826%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22UP%20Officer%20Removed%20From%20Post%20After%20'Punishment'%20Video%20Goes%20Viral%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20government%20official%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Bareilly%20has%20been%20removed%20from%20his%20post%20after%20a%20video%20of%20a%20man%20allegedly%20being%20'punished'%20inside%20his%20office%20went%20viral.%20Udit%20Pawar%2C%20the%20Sub%20Divisional%20Magistrate%20(SDM)%20of%20Mirganj%20town%20in%20Bareilly%20district%2C%20has%20been%20accused%20of%20asking%20a%20man%20to%20'crouch%20like%20a%20chicken'%20after%20he%20reportedly%20visited%20the%20officer%20for%20the%20third%20time%20with%20a%20request%20for%20a%20cremation%20ground.%20Mr%20Pawar%20has%20denied%20the%20charge%2C%20saying%20the%20man%20was%20already%20crouched%20in%20that%20position%20when%20he%20entered%20his%20office%2C%20and%20he%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20asked%20him%20why%20he%20was%20doing%20it%20and%20directed%20others%20present%20there%20to%20help%20him%20to%20his%20feet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20District%20Magistrate%20has%2C%20however%2C%20said%20that%20an%20initial%20enquiry%20has%20revealed%20that%20the%20SDM%20was%20at%20fault.%20He%20has%20removed%20Mr%20Pawar%20from%20his%20post%2C%20and%20not%20assigned%20him%20a%20fresh%20posting%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20victim%20has%20alleged%20that%20he%2C%20along%20with%20some%20others%20from%20his%20village%2C%20reached%20the%20SDM%20office%20with%20a%20demand%20related%20to%20a%20cremation%20ground%2C%20but%20the%20SDM%20punished%20him%20instead%2C%20and%20threw%20away%20his%20letter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20went%20to%20his%20office%20regarding%20the%20cremation%20ground.%20I%20gave%20him%20testimonials%20stating%20there%20is%20no%20cremation%20ground%20in%20Mandanpur%20village.%20SDM%20sir%20punished%20me%20by%20asking%20me%20to%20'crouch%20like%20a%20chicken'.%20When%20I%20asked%20why%20he%20was%20doing%20it%2C%20he%20started%20abusing%20me.%20I%20told%20him%20I%20have%20come%20to%20you%20for%20the%20third%20time%20as%20I%20have%20not%20got%20justice%2C%20and%20I%20will%20keep%20crouching%20like%20this%20till%20I%20get%20justice.%20He%20then%20said%20I%20was%20only%20acting.%20He%20said%20there's%20no%20mention%20of%20a%20cremation%20ground%20in%20official%20documents%2C%20only%20a%20cemetery%20is%20registered%20there%2C%20and%20I%20won't%20get%20any%20justice%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20villager%2C%20Pappu%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20villagers'%20complaint%20letter%20said%20that%20both%20Hindus%20and%20Muslims%20live%20in%20the%20village%2C%20but%20there%20is%20no%20cremation%20ground%20in%20the%20village.%20Some%20people%20of%20the%20Muslim%20community%20have%20captured%20the%20land%20of%20the%20cremation%20ground%20in%20the%20name%20of%20cemetery%2C%20it%20alleged.%20In%20such%20a%20situation%2C%20the%20district%20administration%20should%20arrange%20land%20for%20a%20crematorium%20as%20they%20face%20difficulty%20in%20performing%20the%20last%20rites%2C%20the%20letter%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20SDM%2C%20in%20his%20defence%2C%20said%20he%20noticed%20five%20to%20six%20people%20from%20the%20village%20in%20his%20chamber%20when%20he%20returned%20from%20court%2C%20and%20a%20man%20was%20already%20crouching%20on%20his%20office%20floor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20of%20them%20suddenly%20got%20in%20that%20position%20as%20soon%20as%20he%20saw%20me.%20I%20asked%20him%20why%20he%20was%20doing%20that%2C%20and%20requested%20others%20to%20help%20him%20up.%20Meanwhile%2C%20someone%20shot%20a%20video%20at%20that%20moment%20and%20left.%20I%20listened%20to%20their%20complaint%20and%20also%20asked%20the%20accountant%20to%20settle%20the%20matter.%20The%20allegation%20that%20I%20punished%20that%20man%20is%20not%20true%2C%26quot%3B%20Udit%20Pawar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBareilly's%20District%20Magistrate%20Shivkant%20Dwivedi%2C%20however%2C%20said%20he%20came%20across%20a%20video%20where%20a%20man%20was%20seen%20in%20a%20humiliating%20position%20on%20the%20floor%20of%20Mr%20Pawar's%20office%2C%20and%20an%20enquiry%20found%20the%20officer%20negligent%2C%20after%20which%20he%20was%20immediately%20removed%20from%20his%20post%20and%20a%20new%20officer%20appointed%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694842200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Ficrpah9_mirganj-sdm-udit-pawar_625x300_16_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbareilly-mirganj-sdm-udit-pawar-removed-from-post-after-punishment-video-goes-viral-4394899%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20government%20official%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Bareilly%20has%20been%20removed%20from%20his%20post%20after%20a%20video%20of%20a%20man%20allegedly%20being%20'punished'%20inside%20his%20office%20went%20viral.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbareilly-mirganj-sdm-udit-pawar-removed-from-post-after-punishment-video-goes-viral-4394899%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbareilly-mirganj-sdm-udit-pawar-removed-from-post-after-punishment-video-goes-viral-4394899%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbareilly-mirganj-sdm-udit-pawar-removed-from-post-after-punishment-video-goes-viral-4394899%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Can%20diabetes%20cause%20behavioral%20changes%3F%20Experts%20explain%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694842200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-103707017%2Cimgsize-709059.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Flife-style%2Fhealth-fitness%2Fhealth-news%2Fcan-diabetes-cause-behavioral-changes-experts-expl