3%20A%20Celebration%20of%20Kink%2C%20Queerness%2C%20and%20Cinema%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20experience%20of%20watching%20adult%20cinema%20collectively%2C%20in%20a%20dark%20theatre%2C%20with%20a%20mix%20of%20colleagues%20from%20work%2C%20and%20complete%20strangers%2C%20was%20jarring%20to%20begin%20with.%20At%20the%20first%20few%20instances%20of%20watching%20prolonged%20scenes%20of%20physical%20intimacy%20in%20close%20quarters%2C%20I%20held%20my%20breath%20and%20froze%20in%20my%20seat.%20I%20soon%20realised%20that%20I%20needed%20to%20overcome%20the%20internalised%20self-consciousness%20of%20being%20discovered%20I%20feel%20while%20watching%20sexual%20media%20in%20private.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20In%20the%20slow%20trust%20I%20offered%20the%20space%2C%20I%20witnessed%20its%20unabashed%20capacity%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20discussions%20that%20followed%20the%20films.%C2%A0%20Here%2C%20visual%20erotica%20found%20a%20unique%20purpose%2C%20of%20vulnerability%2C%20introspection%2C%20and%20community-building.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESpectators%20shared%20that%20the%20consumption%20of%20pornography%2C%20and%20its%20utility%2C%20usually%20encourages%20one%20to%20consume%20large%20amounts%20of%20content%2C%20at%20a%20quickened%20pace%2C%20to%20arrive%20at%20the%20suitable%20array%20of%20images%3B%20for%20a%20rhythmic%20anticipation%20towards%20orgasm.%20Here%2C%20whereas%20the%20sensuality%20of%20erotica%20remained%2C%20the%20deliberate%20turning%20on%20of%20lights%2C%20demanded%20an%20inversion%20of%20one%E2%80%99s%20interior%20self%20to%20this%20public.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhereas%20a%20plethora%20of%20experimental%2C%20documentary%2C%20and%20educational%20films%2C%20peaked%20my%20unwavering%20attention%2C%20during%20some%20screenings%2C%20my%20mind%20wandered%20away%2C%20distracted.%20Regardless%20of%20my%20state%20while%20watching%20these%20films%2C%20they%20demanded%20witnessing%2C%20at%20their%20own%20pace%2C%20on%20their%20own%20terms.%20I%20thought%2C%20for%20a%20space%20built%20around%20kink%2C%20this%20was%20the%20ultimate%20exercise%20in%20submission.%20My%20back%20ached%2C%20my%20throat%20became%20dry%2C%20but%20I%20sat%2C%20every%20day%2C%20for%20three%20days%20on%20my%20seat%2C%20watching.%20For%20extended%20periods%2C%20when%20my%20gaze%20was%20arrested%20on%20the%20screen%2C%20I%20learnt%20to%20remind%20myself%20to%20let%20loose%2C%20breathe%2C%20shift%20my%20posture%2C%20crack%20my%20back%20and%20take%20a%20sip%20of%20water.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20someone%20like%20myself%2C%20an%20amateur%20kinkster%2C%20films%20offered%20surprising%20moments%20of%20arousal%2C%20in%20sharing%20a%20breadth%20of%20sexual%20acts%20and%20relationships%20that%20minimised%20normative%2C%20peno-vaginal%20sex.%20Vignettes%20of%20tenderness%20in%20these%20relationships%20felt%20like%20warm%20invitations%20that%20made%20me%20intermittently%20message%20my%20partner%20about%20all%20the%20exciting%20possibilities%20of%20sexual%20and%20romantic%20expression%20we%20could%20weave%20into%20our%20lives.%20In%20the%20film%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCu32DWlSAan%2F%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EBreathtaking%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Cspan%3E(directed%20by%20Morgana%20Muses)%2C%20a%20couple%20indulged%20in%20tender%20breathplay%2C%20where%20the%20dominatrix%20led%20the%20submissive%20to%20luxuriate%20in%20their%20attentive%20care.%20In%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ESpellbound%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(directed%20by%20Ulrike%20Kaffei)%20a%20couple%2C%20crouching%20like%20tigers%2C%20dressed%20in%20black%2C%20tattooed%20extensively%2C%20found%20themselves%20involved%20in%20a%20choreography%20of%20rope-play.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20dominatrix%20entangled%20their%20submissive%20in%20an%20intricate%20spider-web%20of%20bright%20red%20rope%2C%20a%20hypnotic%20sight.%20The%20rope%20that%20suspended%20and%20rendered%20the%20submissive%20immobile%2C%20transformed%20into%20a%20blanket%20to%20engulf%20the%20two%20in%20a%20moment%20of%20emotive%20aftercare.%20In%20the%20curiosity%20of%20playing%20with%20breath%20and%20ropes%2C%20I%20wondered%20about%20my%20own%20anxieties%20surrounding%20claustrophobia%20and%20constriction.%20After%20a%20panicked%20experience%20of%20breathlessness%20during%20a%20diving%20trip%2C%20I%20remembered%20the%20trust%20I%20instilled%20in%20my%20partner%20who%20held%20my%20hand%2C%20and%20slowly%20led%20me%20into%20the%20ocean%20again.%20Over%20time%2C%20I%20learned%20to%20float%20in%20the%20ocean%2C%20first%20with%20the%20support%20of%20his%20arms%2C%20and%20then%2C%20by%20breathing%20deeply%20with%20the%20ocean%E2%80%99s%20waves%20slowly%20lapping%20me%20up%20in%20a%20rhythmic%20trance.%20Watching%20the%20transcendent%20submissives%2C%20I%20was%20reminded%20of%20my%20own%20reintroduction%20to%20the%20ocean%2C%20where%20I%20allowed%20myself%20to%20overcome%20fear%20and%20enter%20a%20meditative%20state%20by%20trusting%20my%20partner%20and%20the%20expansive%20capacity%20of%20my%20body.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20397px)%2085vw%2C%20397px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F16043913%2FScreenshot-2023-09-16-at-4.39.02-AM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22397%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F16043913%2FScreenshot-2023-09-16-at-4.39.02-AM.png%20846w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F16043913%2FScreenshot-2023-09-16-at-4.39.02-AM-212x300.png%20212w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F16043913%2FScreenshot-2023-09-16-at-4.39.02-AM-722x1024.png%20722w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-673257%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22563%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20Mes%20Amours%2C%20directed%20by%20Anoushka.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EApart%20from%20the%20catharsis%20in%20these%20films%2C%20I%20felt%20sheer%20joy%20in%20expressions%20of%20queer%20love%2C%20of%20diverse%20bodies%20moving%2C%20shaking%2C%20thumping%20against%20one%20another.%20Some%20in%20the%20audience%20shared%20an%20ache%20and%20longing%20for%20such%20spaces%20of%20celebration%2C%20while%20others%20felt%20emboldened%20to%20imagine%20utopian%20futures%20replete%20with%20joyous%20promise.%20While%20watching%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Debauchary%20Ball%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(directed%20by%20David%20Weathersby)%20on%20Chicago%E2%80%99s%20annual%20underground%20ceremony%20of%20Black%20kinky%20sexuality%20and%20House%20music%2C%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20stop%20moving%20in%20my%20seat%20to%20the%20electrifying%20beats.%20The%20juxtaposition%20and%20multi-sensorial%20joy%20of%20music%20matching%20the%20colour%20and%20candour%20of%20gyrating%20bodies%2C%20was%20also%20captivating%20in%20the%20film%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EVivante%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%20%3Cspan%3E(directed%20by%20Anoushka).%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESeveral%20films%20shared%20the%20laughter%2C%20chaos%2C%20and%20the%20frolic%20that%20sex%20truly%20reveals%2C%20in%20between%20positions%20and%20moments%20of%20seduction%20and%20pursuit.%20In%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20Weekend%20in%20Germany%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%20%3Cspan%3E(directed%20by%20Jan%20Soldat)%2C%20two%20men%20in%20their%2070s%2C%20live%20a%20relaxed%20life%20of%20kink%2C%20where%20naps%20in%20their%20garden%20are%20followed%20by%20a%20play%20of%20flogging%2C%20spanking%20and%20video-archiving%20their%20sexual%20encounters.%20The%20two%20cajole%20each%20other%20like%20high-school%20boys%2C%20tugging%20on%20each%20other%E2%80%99s%20bodies%2C%20teasing%20each%20other%20through%20their%20day.%20In%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EMILF%20Next%20Door%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%20%3Cspan%3E(directed%20by%20Sadie%20Lune)%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EMy%20Garage%20My%20Rules%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%20%3Cspan%3E(directed%20by%20Manon%20Praline)%2C%20the%20plot%20invoked%20the%20classic%20trope%20of%20porn%20films%2C%20where%20a%20sexual%20encounter%20between%20two%20individuals%20is%20facilitated%20through%20a%20false%20pretext%3B%20a%20jar%20of%20sugar%20from%20the%20next-door%20neighbour%2C%20a%20broken%20car%20awaiting%20repair%20at%20a%20garage.%20Both%20these%20tongue-in-cheek%20premises%20were%20however%2C%20inverted%20in%20the%20films%20with%20a%20non-normative%20cast%20and%20moments%20of%20unpretentious%2C%20unrehearsed%20respite.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20ecstasy%20of%20watching%20these%20films%2C%20it%20was%20sobering%20to%20ponder%20on%20the%20discomforts%20of%20kink%3B%20the%20ambiguities%20around%20relationships%2C%20and%20the%20messiness%20it%20entails%2C%20when%20gone%20awry.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20Least%20I%E2%80%99ve%20Been%20Outside%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(directed%20by%20Jan%20Soldat)%2C%20the%20filmmaker%20shares%20a%20comedic%20screen%20recording%20of%20persons%20on%20a%20dating%20app%2C%20rejecting%20his%20request%20of%20filming%20them%20solo.%20A%20jilted%20lover%2C%20navigates%20marriage%20in%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ESaint%20and%20Whore%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%20%3Cspan%3E(directed%20by%20Anne%20Berchad)%20through%20sacrifice%20and%20endurance%2C%20but%20confronts%20and%20wreaks%20havoc%20in%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EHouse%20for%20Sale%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%20%3Cspan%3E(directed%20by%20Eisha%20Marjara).%20In%20these%20films%2C%20complex%20intersections%20of%20gender%2C%20power%2C%20and%20consent%20provided%20fascinating%20conversation%20among%20the%20attendees%2C%20who%20shared%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20contradictory%20thoughts.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20two%20occasions%2C%20kink%20educator%20Ancilla%20facilitated%20classes%20on%20Erotic%20Expressionism%20and%20Erotic%20Communication%2C%20creating%20an%20opportunity%20for%20the%20sex%20education%20class%2C%20I%20had%20not%20received%20and%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20needed.%20The%20introspective%20questions%20in%20the%20seminar%20provoked%20me%20to%20think%20about%20the%20formative%20interiors%20of%20my%20erotic%20self%2C%20and%20brought%20to%20my%20consciousness%20memories%20and%20glimmers%20of%20sensuality%20from%20the%20past.%20In%20sharing%20experiences%20of%20the%20self%20with%20the%20cohort%2C%20instances%20of%20fondness%2C%20betrayal%2C%20the%20complicity%20of%20the%20self%2C%20came%20to%20the%20fore.%20The%20reflexivity%20of%20the%20attendees%20offered%20an%20opportunity%20to%20participate%20in%20what%20felt%20like%20group%20therapy%2C%20akin%20to%20anonymous%20support%20groups%20that%20I%20have%20observed%20in%20films%20and%20television%20before.%20The%20classes%20offered%20thought%20into%20non-genital%2C%20non-sexual%20eroticism%2C%20such%20as%20the%20sartorial%20choices%20of%20sexual%20aestheticism.%20I%20thought%20about%20my%20love%20for%20the%20sari%2C%20a%20garment%20held%20together%20by%20the%20constriction%20of%20the%20petticoat%2C%20whose%20tight%20knot%20around%20my%20waist%20stimulates%2C%20and%20relieves%2C%20with%20its%20untying%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20very%20location%20of%20the%20festival%20at%20Akshara%20Theatre%20in%20Delhi%20amused%20me.%20The%20venue%20has%20been%20a%20site%20of%20cultural%20memory%2C%20where%20I%20have%20grown%20up%20watching%20plays%20with%20my%20parents%2C%20which%20now%20carries%20a%20re-inscribed%20meaning.%20At%20the%20end%2C%20the%20word%20%E2%80%98edge%2C%E2%80%99%20in%20the%20naming%20of%20the%20festival%2C%20made%20me%20think%20about%20%E2%80%98edging%E2%80%99%2C%20or%20the%20prolonged%20restraining%20of%20climax%2C%20which%20truly%20was%20the%20experience%20of%20watching%20these%20films.%20In%20the%20safety%20and%20warmth%20of%20a%20community%2C%20a%20dark%20theatre%20transformed%20into%20a%20space%20for%20vulnerability%2C%20openness%2C%20and%20sharing%2C%20morning%20to%20evening%20for%20three%20days.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EKali%20is%20a%20researcher%2C%20writer%20and%20teacher%20interested%20in%20legal%20critique%2C%20queerness%2C%20and%20art.%20Their%20anonymity%20arises%20from%20the%20stigma%20and%20shame%20around%20topics%20discussed%20in%20this%20piece.%20They%20dream%20about%20being%20loud%20and%20proud%20one%20day!%20%C2%A0Kali%20volunteers%20with%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fkinkycollective%2F%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EKinky%20Collective%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20an%20activist%20group%20which%20seeks%20to%20raise%20social%20awareness%20about%20kink%20and%20to%20strengthen%20the%20Indian%20BDSM%20community%2C%20which%20can%20be%20contacted%20at%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ethekinkygroup%40gmail.com%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694831452000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F08%2F09151655%2Frape-culture-behaviours.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffilm%2Fa-festival-in-celebration-of-celebration-of-kink-queerness-and-cinema%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20the%20safety%20and%20warmth%20of%20a%20community%2C%20a%20dark%20theatre%20transformed%20into%20a%20space%20for%20vulnerability%2C%20openness%2C%20and%20sharing%2C%20morning%20to%20evening%20for%20three%20days.%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffilm%2Fa-festival-in-celebration-of-celebration-of-kink-queerness-and-cinema%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20Did%20Mohammad%20Akbar%20Lone%20Breach%20His%20Oath%20of%20Allegiance%20to%20the%20Constitution%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F09%2F05160449%2FScreen-Shot-2019-09-05-at-4.04.29-PM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20couple%20of%20weeks%20ago%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20of%20India%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fsupreme-court-reserves-verdict-in-article-370-abrogation-challenge%2Farticle67274228.ece%5C%22%3Ereserved%20its%20judgement%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%20more%20than%2030%20petitions%20which%20have%20challenged%20the%20monumental%20changes%20made%20in%20the%20constitutional%20status%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20in%202019.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20marathon%20proceedings%20before%20the%20constitution%20bench%20comprising%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20and%20four%20senior-most%20judges%20of%20the%20apex%20court%20took%2016%20days%20in%20August%20and%20September%202023%20to%20complete.%20Thanks%20to%20the%20pro-transparency%20approach%20adopted%20by%20the%20court%2C%20these%20proceedings%20like%20those%20of%20other%20matters%20heard%20by%20constitution%20benches%20were%20live-streamed.%20This%20is%20a%20welcome%20change%20from%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsc-alternative-procedure-sealed-cover%5C%22%3Enot-too-distant%20era%20of%20sealed%20cover%20procedures%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Recordings%20are%20preserved%20for%20posterity%20on%20YouTube.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDespite%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20court%20was%20only%20performing%20its%20constitutional%20duty%20in%20order%20to%20dispense%20justice%2C%20the%20immense%20levels%20of%20patience%20displayed%20and%20the%20bench%E2%80%99s%20willingness%20to%20hear%20all%20arguments%20and%20shades%20of%20opinion%20including%20some%20points%20presented%20by%20this%20author%20appearing%20as%20a%20last-minute%20intervenor%2C%20deserves%20admiration.%20The%20judgement%20of%20the%20court%20is%20eagerly%20awaited.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EDemanding%20proof%20of%20a%20petitioner%E2%80%99s%20allegiance%20to%20the%20constitution%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20last%20two%20days%20of%20the%20very%20educative%20proceedings%20were%20marred%20by%20a%20controversy%20that%20arose%20from%20certain%20utterances%20attributed%20to%20Mohammad%20Akbar%20Lone%2C%20one%20of%20the%20lead%20petitioners.%20He%20also%20happens%20to%20be%20a%20sitting%20member%20of%20parliament%20(MP).%20A%20petitioner%20NGO%20brought%20to%20the%20notice%20of%20the%20court%20some%20pro-Pakistani%20slogans%20allegedly%20raised%20by%20Lone%20when%20he%20was%20a%20member%20of%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20legislative%20assembly%2C%20both%20on%20the%20floor%20of%20that%20House%20and%20elsewhere%20in%20public%2C%20a%20few%20years%20ago.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20bench%20insisted%20that%20the%20MP%20file%20an%20affidavit%20stating%20that%20he%20unconditionally%20accepts%20that%20J%26amp%3BK%20is%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20India%20and%20that%20he%20abides%20by%20and%20owes%20allegiance%20to%20the%20constitution%20of%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwho-is-mohammad-akbar-lone%5C%22%3EWho%20is%20Mohammad%20Akbar%20Lone%2C%20the%20Politician%20Asked%20by%20the%20SC%20to%20File%20an%20Allegiance%20Affidavit%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHis%20counsel%20Senior%20Advocate%20Kapil%20Sibal%E2%80%99s%20plea%20that%20the%20remarks%20had%20been%20expunged%20from%20the%20record%20of%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20assembly%20debates%20and%20that%20that%20the%20MP%20had%20sworn%20an%20oath%20of%20allegiance%20to%20the%20constitution%20of%20India%20while%20entering%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20did%20not%20cut%20much%20ice%20with%20the%20court.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20bench%20reasoned%20that%20when%20the%20MP%20invokes%20the%20jurisdiction%20of%20the%20court%20under%20Article%2032%20of%20the%20constitution%2C%20he%20is%20required%20to%20abide%20by%20and%20owe%20allegiance%20to%20the%20constitution%20like%20every%20other%20Indian.%20The%20bench%20also%20said%20that%20it%20was%20willing%20to%20hear%20the%20MP%20like%20all%20other%20petitioners%20from%20J%26amp%3BK%20who%20came%20before%20them%20as%20it%20is%20their%20duty%2C%20but%20he%20must%20file%20a%20one-page%20affidavit%20avowing%20his%20allegiance%20to%20the%20constitution%20and%20to%20the%20fact%20that%20J%26amp%3BK%20is%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20India%20because%20of%20the%20contents%20of%20the%20affidavit%20that%20has%20been%20submitted%20to%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20the%20last%20day%20of%20the%20proceedings%2C%20the%20MP%20filed%20an%20affidavit%20avowing%20that%20he%20is%20a%20responsible%20and%20dutiful%20citizen%20of%20the%20Union%20of%20India%20and%20that%20he%20has%20exercised%20his%20right%20to%20approach%20the%20court%20through%20Article%2032%20of%20the%20constitution.%20He%20also%20reiterated%20the%20oath%20he%20took%20while%20being%20sworn%20in%20as%20an%20MP%20to%20preserve%20and%20uphold%20the%20provision%20of%20the%20constitution%20of%20India%20and%20to%20protect%20the%20territorial%20integrity%20of%20the%20nation.%20As%20objections%20were%20voiced%20to%20the%20affidavit%E2%80%99s%20contents%20that%20it%20did%20not%20contain%20an%20express%20disavowal%20of%20terrorism%20and%20separatism%2C%20the%20Court%20assured%20that%20it%20would%20analyse%20the%20affidavit%20later%20on.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20do%20not%20intend%20to%20question%20the%20wisdom%20of%20the%20court%20in%20dealing%20with%20the%20controversy.%20However%2C%20the%20solution%20prescribed%20by%20the%20court%20to%20end%20the%20controversy%20has%20far%20reaching%20implications%20for%20not%20just%20public%20servants%20such%20as%20MPs%2C%20MLAs%2C%20MLCs%2C%20but%20every%20occupant%20of%20public%20office%20who%20is%20required%20to%20swear%20an%20oath%20of%20allegiance%20to%20the%20constitution.%20This%20is%20what%20I%20would%20like%20to%20comment%20on%20with%20deep%20respect%20to%20the%20dignity%20and%20majesty%20of%20the%20court.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EOath-taking%20requirements%20under%20the%20law%20while%20contesting%20elections%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFirst%2C%20let%20us%20examine%20the%20legal%20requirements%20for%20oath%20taking%20as%20laid%20down%20for%20MPs%20and%20state%20legislators.%20According%20to%20Article%2084%20of%20the%20constitution%20of%20India%2C%20any%20person%20who%20intends%20to%20contest%20elections%20to%20parliament%20must%2C%20first%20and%20foremost%20be%20a%20citizen%20of%20India.%20The%20minimum%20age%20limit%20to%20contest%20elections%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20is%2025%20years%20whereas%20one%20has%20to%20be%20at%20least%2030%20years%20old%20to%20contest%20elections%20for%20a%20Rajya%20Sabha%20seat.%20Next%2C%20the%20constitution%20requires%20such%20aspirants%20to%20subscribe%20an%20oath%20of%20allegiance%20to%20the%20constitution%20of%20India%20and%20uphold%20its%20sovereignty%20and%20integrity%20according%20to%20the%20format%20laid%20down%20in%20the%20Third%20Schedule%20of%20the%20constitution%20before%20any%20person%20authorised%20by%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESimilarly%2C%20an%20MLA%20or%20MLC%20aspirant%20is%20also%20required%20to%20swear%20an%20oath%20or%20solemnly%20affirm%20allegiance%20to%20the%20constitution%20of%20India%20and%20commit%20to%20uphold%20its%20sovereignty%20and%20integrity%2C%20as%20per%20Article%20173.%20A%20format%20for%20this%20oath%20is%20also%20set%20out%20in%20the%20Third%20Schedule.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Handbook%20for%20Returning%20Officers%20published%20by%20the%20Election%20Commission%2C%20the%20format%20of%20this%20oath%20is%20required%20to%20be%20signed%20by%20the%20candidate%20at%20the%20time%20of%20filing%20the%20nomination%20papers.%20The%20authorised%20officer%20before%20whom%20this%20oath%20is%20made%20is%20required%20to%20hand%20over%20a%20certificate%20for%20the%20receipt%20of%20such%20oath%2C%20mentioning%20the%20date%20and%20hour%20at%20which%20the%20candidate%20swore%20the%20oath.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20text%20of%20these%20oaths%20implies%20that%20an%20aspirant%20to%20a%20seat%20in%20either%20parliament%20or%20a%20state%20legislature%20must%20swear%20an%20oath%20of%20allegiance%20to%20the%20constitution%20and%20commit%20to%20uphold%20India%E2%80%99s%20sovereignty%20and%20integrity%20first%20and%20foremost%20at%20the%20time%20of%20contesting%20the%20relevant%20elections.%20According%20to%20the%20Election%20Commission%E2%80%99s%20Handbook%2C%20the%20Returning%20Officer%20may%20reject%20a%20candidate%E2%80%99s%20nomination%20on%20the%20ground%20that%20the%20oath%20or%20affirmation%20is%20not%20made%20in%20accordance%20with%20the%20Constitution.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20until%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20October%2031%2C%202019%2C%20the%20format%20of%20oath%20of%20allegiance%20applicable%20to%20an%20aspirant%20to%20a%20seat%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%20State%20Legislature%20was%20provided%20in%20the%20erstwhile%20J%26amp%3BK%20constitution.%20According%20to%20Section%2051%20of%20this%20document%2C%20an%20aspirant%20to%20a%20seat%20in%20the%20erstwhile%20J%26amp%3BK%20legislative%20assembly%20or%20the%20legislative%20council%20was%20required%20to%20be%20a%20permanent%20resident%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%20with%20minimum%20age%20qualifications%20similar%20to%20that%20prescribed%20for%20the%20membership%20of%20parliament.%20The%20aspirant%20was%20required%20to%20swear%20an%20oath%20or%20make%20an%20affirmation%20as%20laid%20down%20in%20the%20Fifth%20Schedule%20of%20the%20erstwhile%20J%26amp%3BK%20constitution%20before%20an%20officer%20authorised%20by%20the%20Election%20Commission.%20The%20J%26amp%3BK%20constitution%20did%20not%20provide%20for%20a%20separate%20election%20management%20body%20for%20conducting%20these%20elections.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20format%20of%20the%20oath%20or%20affirmation%20is%20reproduced%20below%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%2C%20A.%20B.%2C%20having%20been%20nominated%20as%20a%20candidate%20to%20fill%20a%20seat%20in%20the%20Legislative%20Assembly%2C%20(or%20Legislative%20Council)%20do%20swear%20in%20the%20name%20of%20God%2Fsolemnly%20affirm%20that%20I%20will%20bear%20true%20faith%E2%80%99%20and%20allegiance%20to%20the%20Constitution%20of%20the%20State%20as%20by%20law%20established%20and%20that%20I%20will%20uphold%20the%20sovereignty%20and%20integrity%20of%20India%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Election%20Commission%E2%80%99s%20Handbook%20for%20Returning%20Officers%2C%20the%20nomination%20papers%20of%20a%20candidate%20for%20elections%20to%20the%20erstwhile%20J%26amp%3BK%20legislature%20could%20be%20rejected%20for%20not%20being%20accompanied%20by%20an%20oath%2Faffirmation%20signed%20by%20him%2Fher%20in%20the%20manner%20prescribed%20by%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESome%20hasty%20readers%20might%20point%20out%20that%20the%20aforementioned%20format%20of%20oath%20does%20not%20mention%20the%20constitution%20of%20India%20and%20is%20therefore%20not%20adequate.%20Adopting%20such%20a%20position%20would%20be%20fallacious%20because%20the%20definitions%20clause%20contained%20in%20Section%202(1)(a)%20of%20the%20erstwhile%20J%26amp%3BK%20constitution%20clearly%20referred%20to%20and%20explained%20the%20%E2%80%9CConstitution%20of%20India%E2%80%9D%20as%20follows%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9C%E2%80%9CConstitution%20of%20India%E2%80%9D%20means%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India%20as%20applicable%20in%20relation%20to%20this%20State%3B%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20phrase%20%E2%80%93%20%E2%80%9Cas%20applicable%E2%80%9D%20obviously%20connoted%20the%20length%2C%20breadth%2C%20scope%20and%20extent%20of%20the%20applicability%20of%20the%20constitution%20of%20India%20as%20laid%20down%20under%20Article%20370%2C%20until%20it%20was%20amended%20in%202019.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESo%2C%20the%20phrase%20%E2%80%9CConstitution%20of%20the%20State%E2%80%9D%20must%20be%20understood%20as%20including%20all%20such%20parts%20of%20the%20constitution%20of%20India%20that%20were%20made%20applicable%20to%20J%26amp%3BK%20vide%20the%20presidential%20orders%20issued%20under%20Article%20370(1)%20until%202019.%20Any%20other%20restrictive%20interpretation%20would%20not%20only%20be%20political%20in%20its%20approach%20but%20also%20mischievous%20in%20intent.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EOath-taking%20requirements%20under%20the%20law%20after%20winning%20elections%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EArticle%2099%20of%20the%20constitution%20of%20India%20requires%20every%20elected%20or%20nominated%20member%20of%20parliament%20to%20subscribe%20an%20oath%20or%20make%20an%20affirmation%20before%20taking%20his%2Fher%20seat%20in%20either%20House.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EArticle%20188%20of%20the%20constitution%20of%20India%20similarly%20requires%20every%20person%20elected%20or%20nominated%20to%20the%20state%20legislature%20to%20subscribe%20an%20oath%20or%20make%20an%20affirmation%20before%20taking%20his%2Fher%20seat%20in%20either%20House.%20The%20format%20of%20the%20oath%20to%20be%20made%20before%20the%20governor%20of%20the%20state%20or%20a%20person%20authorised%20by%20him%20as%20provided%20in%20the%20Third%20Schedule%20is%20similar%20to%20the%20text%20reproduced%20above%20except%20in%20its%20reference%20to%20the%20name%20of%20the%20house%20of%20the%20state%20legislature.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20case%20of%20the%20erstwhile%20J%26amp%3BK%20constitution%2C%20the%20requirement%20of%20subscribing%20an%20oath%20or%20making%20an%20affirmation%20by%20a%20newly%20elected%20MLA%20or%20MLC%20is%20provided%20in%20Section%2064.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EHow%20many%20times%20has%20Lone%20taken%20the%20oath%20of%20allegiance%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENow%20that%20we%20have%20clarity%20about%20the%20legal%20requirements%20for%20MPs%20and%20MLAs%20regarding%20the%20oath%20of%20allegiance%20to%20the%20constitution%20they%20need%20to%20take%2C%20it%20would%20be%20worthwhile%20to%20examine%20how%20many%20times%20Lone%20has%20officially%20subscribed%20to%20this%20oath%20till%20date.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20twin%20parliamentary%20websites%20publish%20the%20profile%20of%20siting%20and%20former%20members.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20According%20to%20the%20profile%20page%20of%20Lone%2C%20he%20was%20elected%20MP%20from%20Baramulla%20constituency%2C%20J%26amp%3BK%20in%20May%202019.%20So%20that%20would%20have%20required%20him%20to%20take%20the%20oath%20of%20allegiance%20to%20the%20constitution%20and%20to%20uphold%20the%20sovereignty%20and%20integrity%20of%20India%20%3C%2Fspan%3Etwice%2C%20%3Cspan%3Eonce%20at%20the%20time%20of%20filing%20nominations%20and%20then%20before%20taking%20his%20seat%20in%20the%20house.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20this%20profile%20page%20indicates%20that%20he%20was%20a%20member%20of%20the%20erstwhile%20J%26amp%3BK%20Legislative%20Assembly%20for%20three%20terms%20since%20the%20year%202002.%20So%20as%20each%20term%20would%20have%20required%20him%20to%20subscribe%20to%20the%20oath%20of%20allegiance%20to%20the%20constitution%20twice%2C%20he%20would%20have%20complied%20with%20this%20constitutional%20requirement%20six%20times%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20makes%20it%20a%20total%20of%20eight%20times%20that%20he%20subscribed%20to%20the%20oath%20to%20the%20constitution%20since%202002.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThat%20is%20not%20all.%20According%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20website%2C%20Lone%20also%20served%20as%20the%20Minister%20for%20Higher%20Education%20in%20the%20erstwhile%20state%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%20between%202013-14.%20Section%2040%20of%20the%20erstwhile%20constitution%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%20requires%20every%20minister%20to%20be%20administered%20an%20oath%20of%20office%20and%20secrecy%20by%20the%20governor%20before%20he%2Fshe%20enters%20office.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWithout%20a%20doubt%2C%20Lone%20would%20have%20subscribed%20to%20this%20oath%20of%20allegiance%20to%20the%20constitution%20(which%20implies%20allegiance%20to%20the%20constitution%20of%20India%20as%20well)%20and%20committed%20himself%20to%20uphold%20the%20sovereignty%20and%20integrity%20of%20India%20before%20entering%20the%20office%20of%20minister%20in%20J%26amp%3BK.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20all%20included%2C%20Lone%20is%20publicly%20known%20to%20have%20sworn%20allegiance%20to%20the%20constitution%20and%20committed%20himself%20to%20uphold%20the%20sovereignty%20and%20integrity%20of%20India%20a%20total%20of%20nine%20times%20since%202002%20until%20the%20day%20controversy%20arose%20before%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20while%20hearing%20the%20Article%20370%20matter%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFrom%20the%20recording%20of%20the%20constitution%20bench%20proceedings%20and%20later%20the%20transcript%20of%20the%20exchanges%20published%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20it%20appears%20that%20its%20attention%20was%20not%20drawn%20to%20eight%20out%20of%20the%20nine%20times%20Lone%20took%20the%20oath%20of%20allegiance%20and%20committed%20himself%20to%20protect%20the%20sovereignty%20and%20integrity%20of%20India.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20course%20of%20the%20heated%20debate%20his%20counsel%20was%20able%20to%20recall%20only%20one%20occasion%20when%20he%20took%20such%20an%20oath%20i.e.%2C%20before%20taking%20his%20seat%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20after%20being%20elected.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EFurther%2C%20the%20fact%20that%20he%20had%20taken%20the%20oath%20of%20allegiance%20to%20the%20constitution%20at%20least%20twice%20after%20the%202018%20utterances%20attributed%20to%20him%20also%20was%20not%20pointed%20out%20by%20his%20counsel%20or%20anybody%20else%20present%20in%20the%20court.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EQuestions%20that%20the%20controversy%20throws%20up%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBe%20that%20as%20it%20may%2C%20it%20is%20difficult%20to%20label%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20instructions%20that%20Lone%20file%20an%20affidavit%20swearing%20allegiance%20to%20the%20constitution%20as%20a%20knee-jerk%20reaction%20because%20of%20the%20manner%20in%20which%20it%20was%20insisted%20upon.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20given%20the%20nature%20of%20court%20proceedings%2C%20until%20a%20party%20formally%20submits%20the%20points%20of%20law%20and%20facts%20described%20in%20the%20pervious%20segment%20of%20this%20note%2C%20the%20court%20is%20not%20expected%20to%20take%20judicial%20notice%20of%20the%20same.%20Given%20the%20deadline%20stipulated%20for%20completing%20the%20proceedings%20on%20the%2016%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eth%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20day%2C%20there%20was%20not%20enough%20time%20to%20drawn%20the%20attention%20of%20the%20bench%20to%20these%20matters.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EExperts%20in%20constitutional%20law%20and%20fundamental%20rights%20jurisprudence%20have%20pointed%20out%20that%20certain%20fundamental%20rights%20like%20the%20rights%20to%20equality%2C%20life%20and%20liberty%20and%20the%20right%20to%20approach%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20when%20these%20rights%20are%20breached%20by%20the%20actions%20or%20omissions%20of%20state%20functionaries%20are%20available%20to%20any%20person%20including%20non-citizens.%20They%20have%20opined%20that%20it%20would%20be%20undesirable%20if%20the%20Lone%20case%20sets%20a%20trend%20of%20insisting%20on%20non-citizens%20to%20swear%20allegiance%20to%20the%20constitution%20as%20a%20prerequisite%20before%20approaching%20the%20apex%20court%20for%20justice.%20I%20have%20little%20to%20add%20to%20this%20category%20of%20responses.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20my%20view%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cb%3Efirst%20question%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20the%20court%E2%80%99s%20manner%20of%20treating%20Lone%20throws%20up%20is%20what%20actions%20or%20omissions%20of%20an%20MP%2C%20MLA%20or%20MLC%20constitute%20a%20breach%20their%20oath%20of%20allegiance%20to%20the%20Constitution%20and%20to%20uphold%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20sovereignty%20and%20territorial%20integrity.%20The%20constitution%20of%20India%20is%20silent%20on%20this%20issue.%20I%20strongly%2C%20believe%20that%20not%20only%20these%20elected%20representatives%20but%20we%20the%20citizens%20who%20elect%20them%2C%20have%20the%20right%20to%20know.%20I%20hope%20the%20court%20clarifies%20this%20matter%20at%20a%20not-too-distant%20date.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cb%3E%20second%20question%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20arises%20from%20the%20controversy%20is%20about%20the%20consequences%20that%20might%20arise%20from%20the%20breach%20of%20such%20oaths%20of%20allegiance%20and%20the%20remedial%20action%20that%20is%20required%20to%20be%20taken.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWill%20the%20submission%20of%20an%20affidavit%20swearing%20allegiance%20be%20adequate%3F%20Is%20it%20even%20necessary%3F%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20constitution%20is%20silent%20on%20this%20issue%20as%20well.%20I%20am%20not%20even%20questioning%20the%20power%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20to%20insist%20upon%20the%20filing%20of%20such%20an%20affidavit%2C%20like%20some%20legal%20experts%20have%20done.%20I%20am%20assuming%20that%20the%20plenary%20and%20implied%20powers%20of%20the%20court%20make%20such%20action%20permissible.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20case%20of%20Lone%2C%20the%20court%20deemed%20it%20adequate%20to%20require%20him%20to%20submit%20an%20affidavit%20swearing%20allegiance%20to%20the%20constitution%20and%20India%E2%80%99s%20sovereignty%20and%20territorial%20integrity%20to%20prove%20his%20loyalty.%20If%20this%20is%20indeed%20a%20substantive%20remedial%20measure%2C%20did%20the%20swearing%20of%20the%20oath%20of%20allegiance%20before%20contesting%20elections%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20thereafter%20while%20taking%20his%20seat%20in%20the%20House%2C%20not%20once%20but%20twice%2C%20not%20have%20a%20similar%20effect%3F%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOr%20do%20such%20remedial%20measures%20become%20effective%20only%20when%20executed%20in%20response%20to%20a%20charge%20that%20casts%20doubt%20over%20a%20person%E2%80%99s%20allegiance%20to%20the%20Constitution%20and%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20sovereignty%3F%20If%20this%20is%20the%20cause-effect%20relationship%20between%20the%20charge%20made%20and%20the%20expiatory%20action%20that%20must%20follow%2C%20does%20the%20swearing%20of%20such%20an%20oath%20before%20and%20after%20successfully%20contesting%20elections%20become%20a%20mere%20procedural%20formality%20with%20little%20relevance%20after%20the%20purpose%20is%20served%3F%20If%20this%20is%20the%20case%2C%20are%20not%20these%20procedures%20quite%20hollow%20and%20devoid%20of%20substance%3F%20What%20then%20is%20the%20true%20test%20of%20loyalty%20to%20the%20constitution%20and%20respect%20for%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20sovereignty%20and%20territorial%20integrity%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cb%3Ethird%20question%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20arises%20as%20a%20corollary%20to%20the%20second%20one%20is%20whether%20only%20utterances%20such%20as%20that%20which%20constitute%20the%20basis%20of%20the%20current%20controversy%20are%20liable%20to%20be%20treated%20a%20breach%20of%20oath%20of%20allegiance%3F%20Or%20are%20there%20other%20kinds%20of%20speech%2C%20action%20or%20omission%20that%20may%20also%20qualify%20as%20breach%20of%20such%20an%20oath.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20example%2C%20when%20an%20MP%20or%20MLA%20spews%20forth%20hate%20speech%20targeting%20a%20particular%20community%2C%20does%20he%2Fshe%20also%20breach%20the%20oath%20of%20allegiance%20to%20the%20constitution%20in%20addition%20to%20committing%20a%20criminal%20offence%3F%20If%20so%2C%20what%20is%20the%20penitential%20action%20that%20he%2Fshe%20must%20take%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDoes%20a%20Governor%20breach%20his%20oath%20of%20allegiance%20to%20the%20constitution%20by%20not%20using%20his%2Fher%20powers%20to%20prevent%20a%20change%20in%20government%20through%20horse-trading%20of%20elected%20representatives%3F%20Under%20Article%20159%20of%20the%20constitution%2C%20governors%20also%20subscribe%20an%20oath%20to%20defend%20and%20protect%20the%20constitution.%20How%20are%20they%20to%20atone%20for%20such%20breaches%3F%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EDoes%20the%20immunity%20from%20prosecution%20guaranteed%20for%20governors%20for%20their%20actions%2C%20while%20holding%20office%20guaranteed%20under%20Article%20361%20of%20the%20constitution%2C%20come%20in%20the%20way%20of%20prescribing%20any%20remedial%20action%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20the%20police%20personnel%20stand%20inert%20watching%20blood-thirsty%20mobs%20that%20lynch%20crime%20suspects%20or%20rabidly%20communal%20mobs%20which%20commit%20rape%2C%20murder%2C%20mayhem%20and%20arson%20without%20raising%20a%20finger%20to%20quell%20such%20violence%2C%20are%20they%20breaching%20their%20oath%20of%20allegiance%20to%20the%20constitution%20to%20which%20they%20subscribed%20at%20the%20time%20of%20entering%20the%20service%20as%20per%20the%20civil%20service%20conduct%20rules%20applicable%20to%20them%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3EOr%20when%20law%20enforcement%20agencies%20torture%20crimes%20suspects%20or%20witnesses%20to%20the%20point%20of%20maiming%20them%20or%20even%20causing%20death%2C%20is%20the%20oath%20of%20allegiance%20to%20the%20constitution%20breached%3F%20Prosecuting%20such%20cases%20is%20an%20uphill%20task%2C%20according%20to%20the%20experience%20of%20survivors%20of%20such%20atrocities%20or%20human%20rights%20defenders%20who%20help%20in%20their%20quest%20for%20justice.%20If%20and%20when%20such%20prosecutions%20are%20successful%2C%20will%20the%20accused%20personnel%20be%20required%20to%20take%20an%20oath%20of%20allegiance%20to%20the%20Constitution%3F%20If%20so%2C%20when%3F%20If%20human%20rights%20commissions%20award%20compensation%20to%20survivors%20which%20itself%20indicates%20that%20the%20complaints%20of%20such%20police%20misbehaviour%20are%20true%2C%20is%20the%20breach%20of%20the%20oath%20of%20allegiance%20to%20the%20constitution%20proven%3F%20If%20the%20personnel%20complained%20against%20are%20subsequently%20not%20prosecuted%2C%20will%20they%20be%20required%20to%20be%20swear%20another%20oath%20of%20allegiance%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20controversy%20witnessed%20during%20the%20last%20two%20days%20of%20the%20hearing%20in%20the%20Article%20370%20matter%20and%20the%20court%E2%80%99s%20response%20to%20the%20same%20have%20far%20reaching%20implications%20about%20the%20constitutionally%20appropriate%20conduct%20that%20is%20expected%20from%20the%20holders%20of%20public%20office.%20It%20is%20hoped%20that%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20will%20dwell%20on%20these%20matters%20at%20length%20by%20going%20beyond%20the%20facts%20and%20circumstances%20of%20this%20controversy.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EVenkatesh%20Nayak%20is%20an%20advocate%20of%20transparency%20and%20history%20researcher%20who%20divides%20his%20time%20between%20New%20Delhi%20and%20Bengaluru.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694831407000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F09%2F05160449%2FScreen-Shot-2019-09-05-at-4.04.29-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Farticle-370-akbar-lone-allegiance-to-constitution%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20controversy%20witnessed%20during%20the%20last%20two%20days%20of%20