f%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F304986%2Fkerala-aluva-seed-farm-first-in-india-to-become-carbon-neutral%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewhy%20it%20is%20Kerala%3C%2Fa%3E%20where%20these%20cases%20are%20first%20diagnosed.%20Dr%20Kumar%20attributes%20this%20to%20the%20excellent%20healthcare%20surveillance%20system%20in%20the%20state%20which%20is%20responsible%20for%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20been%20evaluating%20rare%20viruses%20thanks%20to%20our%20quick%20diagnosis.%20We%20have%20a%20great%20public%20healthcare%20system.%20We%20contain%20diseases%20fast%20due%20to%20swift%20action%20in%20any%20unusual%20fever%20cases.%20Private%20clinicians%20work%20closely%20with%20the%20government%20health%20department%20which%20prevents%20the%20disease%20from%20spreading%20further%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%20doctor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694789032000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D330112%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Dr%20Anoop%20Kumar%20AS%2C%20critical%20care%20specialist%20in%20Kozhikode%2C%20was%20part%20of%20the%20teams%20that%20were%20able%20to%20diagnose%20Nipah%20virus%20with%20their%20quick%20thinking%20and%20swift%20action.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F330112%2Fnipah-virus-dr-anoop-kumar-diagnosis-bats-kozhikode-kerala%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Kept%20Its%20Soul%20Intact%E2%80%99%3A%20How%20a%20Kerala%20Architect%20Renovated%20Her%20100-YO%20Home%20With%20Rs%2030%20Lakh%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ENestled%20in%20between%20cocoa%20plantations%20and%20greenery%20with%20no%20houses%20seen%20within%20a%20mile%2C%20Anupa%20Kurian%20grew%20up%20in%20a%20green%20oasis.%20For%20most%20of%20her%20childhood%2C%20she%20grew%20up%20in%20a%20traditional%20Kottayam-styled%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELaced%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F314288%2Fkochi-architect-koshy-builds-office-with-discarded-mangalore-tiles-repurposed-wood-steel%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMangalore%20tiles%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20traditional%20architecture%2C%20the%20house%2C%20as%20per%20Anupa%2C%20%E2%80%9Chas%20a%20soul%20that%20needs%20to%20be%20kept%20intact.%E2%80%9D%20So%20when%20the%20time%20to%20renovate%20the%20100-year-old%20residence%20came%2C%20Anupa%2C%20an%20architect%20and%20designer%2C%20knew%20where%20to%20look%20for%20inspiration.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20knew%20I%20was%20not%20going%20to%20bring%20it%20down%20and%20make%20it%20modern%20but%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F247372%2Fkerala-ecofriendly-sustainable-low-cost-home-ashokan-padapelly-fisherman-him16%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20incorporate%20modern%20amenities%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewhile%20keeping%20the%20authenticity%20of%20the%20house.%20I%20did%20not%20have%20to%20look%20anywhere%20for%20inspiration%2C%20the%20bones%20and%20structure%20of%20the%20house%20were%20inspiration%20enough%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says%20in%20a%20conversation%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20you%20step%20into%20the%20house%20today%2C%20everything%20around%20you%20changes.%20It%20isn%E2%80%99t%202023%20anymore%2C%20but%20you%20are%20transported%20back%20to%20the%20early%201900s.%20Everything%20from%20the%20flooring%20and%20the%20house%E2%80%99s%20layout%20to%20the%20furniture%20gives%20a%20glimpse%20of%20the%20bygone%20era.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EModernising%20the%20house%20while%20preserving%20its%20authenticity%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBorn%20and%20raised%20in%20Kottayam%2C%20Kerala%2C%20the%2031-year-old%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CEven%20as%20a%20kid%2C%20I%20was%20very%20attracted%20to%20designing%20things%20and%20repurposing%20old%20objects.%20This%20interest%20later%20flourished%20into%20a%20passion.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20completing%20her%20graduation%20in%20design%2C%20Anupa%20moved%20to%20the%20UK%20to%20get%20a%20master%E2%80%99s%20degree.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20love%20nature.%20I%20have%20always%20been%20inclined%20towards%20sustainable%20living%20and%20design.%20So%20doing%20a%20master%E2%80%99s%20in%20sustainable%20design%20looked%20like%20the%20right%20choice%20for%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20notes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHaving%20worked%20in%20the%20field%20for%20a%20while%20now%2C%20when%20it%20came%20to%20renovating%20her%20own%20house%2C%20she%20was%20sure%20about%20two%20things%20%E2%80%94%20to%20keep%20the%20house%20as%20authentic%20as%20possible%20and%20use%20sustainable%20means%20to%20do%20so.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20sitting%20on%20a%203%2C000%20sq%20ft%20area%2C%20Pullolickel%20Veedu%20is%20an%20outstanding%20example%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F300504%2Fsustainable-home-in-kerala-made-with-old-stones-and-reused-wood-without-cutting-trees%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esustainability%20and%20traditionality.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20840px)%20100vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fveedu-1-1-1-1694786484.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Anupa%20wanted%20to%20keep%20the%20house%20as%20authentic%20as%20possible%20and%20use%20sustainable%20means%20to%20do%20so%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fveedu-1-1-1-1694786484.jpg%20840w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fveedu-1-1-1-1694786484-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fupload