%20local%20officers%20used%20to%20come%20to%20me%20to%20get%20hens%20and%20eggs%20for%20free%20on%20a%20regular%20basis.%20If%20denied%2C%20they%20would%20provoke%20neighbours%20to%20complain%20against%20me%20for%20bad%20odour%20coming%20from%20my%20poultry%20farm%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20than%20this%2C%20he%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CUsually%2C%20the%20Government%20announces%20compensation%20when%20farmers%20experience%20crop%20losses.%20For%20this%2C%20%3Cem%3Epatwari%20%3C%2Fem%3E(village%20registrar)%20is%20appointed%20to%20survey%20the%20damage.%20In%20the%20process%2C%20they%20seek%20a%20share%20in%20the%20compensation%20amount.%20If%20somebody%20refuses%20to%20give%20the%20amount%2C%20they%20remove%20their%20names%20from%20the%20list.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERavindra%20says%20he%20was%20able%20to%20highlight%20these%20challenges%20in%20front%20of%20IAS%20trainees%20at%20LBSNAA.%20He%20also%20advised%20them%20to%20not%20rely%20on%20junior%20officers%20only%2C%20and%20to%20visit%20farmers%E2%80%99%20sites%20on%20their%20own%20to%20understand%20the%20challenges%20at%20the%20grassroots%20independently.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFarmers%20will%20not%20be%20able%20to%20progress%20with%20farming%20alone.%20After%20sowing%2C%20it%20takes%20five%20months%20to%20generate%20income%20from%20the%20crop.%20During%20this%20period%2C%20they%20are%20left%20without%20any%20means%20to%20earn.%20So%2C%20officers%20should%20encourage%20farmers%20to%20adopt%20parallel%20businesses%20like%20poultry%20farming%2C%20mushroom%20farming%2C%20silk%20and%20cattle%20rearing%2C%20and%20vermicompost%20business%20to%20boost%20their%20income.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERavindra%20shares%20that%20it%20was%20crucial%20for%20him%20to%20put%20forward%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20expectations%20to%20these%20future%20officers%2C%20and%20to%20be%20able%20to%20have%20received%20this%20opportunity%20felt%20like%20a%20great%20achievement.%20%E2%80%9CAt%20LBSNAA%2C%20reputed%20officers%20lecture%20the%20IAS%20trainees.%20And%20that%20day%2C%20a%20farmer%20was%20able%20to%20take%20the%20stage.%20I%20hope%20with%20my%20work%2C%20younger%20generations%20do%20not%20feel%20hesitant%20to%20seek%20a%20career%20in%20farming%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3B%20%3Cem%3EAll%20photos%3A%20Ravindra%20Metkar.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694613032000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Famravati-2-1694610828.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D329814%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Starting%20poultry%20farming%20at%20the%20age%20of%2016%2C%20today%2C%20Ravindra%20Metkar%20(55)%20owns%201.8%20lakh%20hens%20on%20his%20farm%20spread%20across%2050%20acres%20in%20Amravati%2C%20Maharashtra%2C%20earning%20Rs%2060%2C000%20per%20day.%20The%20poultry%20farmer%20was%20invited%20to%20share%20his%20success%20story%20with%20189%20IAS%20trainees.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A41%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F329814%2Famravati-ravindra-metkar-poultry-farmer-success-story-lecture-ias-trainees-lbsnaa-mussoorie%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%227%20Years%20Later%3A%20Inside%20The%20Workings%20of%20Assam%20School%20That%20Accepts%20Plastic%20As%20Fees%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPicture%20this%20%E2%80%93%20every%20Friday%2C%20students%20of%20the%20Akshar%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F307292%2Futtam-teron-parijat-academy-free-education-skill-development-for-poor-children-assam-school%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESchool%20in%20Assam%3C%2Fa%3E%20congregate%20like%20eco-warriors%20on%20a%20mission.%20They%20arrive%2C%20bearing%20a%20week%E2%80%99s%20worth%20of%20collected%20plastic%2C%20their%20hands%20and%20pockets%20filled%20with%20di