.%20%E2%80%9CI%20saw%20this%20(Devra)%20as%20an%20opportunity%20to%20cultivate%20a%20generation%20that%20is%20acutely%20aware%20of%20their%20surroundings.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98What%20is%20stopping%20you%20from%20making%20the%20dream%20come%20true%3F%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%202229px)%20100vw%2C%202229px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FIMG_7362-1_11zon-1694171749.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222229%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22At%20Devra%20the%20local%20women%20of%20Udaipur%20get%20a%20chance%20to%20showcase%20their%20skills%20while%20earning%20a%20livelihood%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FIMG_7362-1_11zon-1694171749.jpg%202229w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FIMG_7362-1_11zon-1694171749-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FIMG_7362-1_11zon-1694171749-500x333.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FIMG_7362-1_11zon-1694171749-768x512.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FIMG_7362-1_11zon-1694171749-1536x1024.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FIMG_7362-1_11zon-1694171749-2048x1365.jpg%202048w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FIMG_7362-1_11zon-1694171749-150x100.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-329449%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221486%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAt%20Devra%20the%20local%20women%20of%20Udaipur%20get%20a%20chance%20to%20showcase%20their%20skills%20while%20earning%20a%20livelihood%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Jyoti%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20they%20first%20began%20working%20out%20of%20this%20land%2C%20they%20started%20floriculture%20with%20the%20idea%20of%20supplying%20flowers%20to%20the%20Taj%20Palace%2C%20Udaipur.%20However%2C%20what%20they%20estimated%20to%20be%20a%20booming%20business%20did%20not%20work%20out.%20They%20had%20hit%20a%20dead%20end.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20the%20couple%20moved%20to%20Delhi%20in%201997%2C%20where%20their%20baby%20girl%20was%20born%2C%20and%20Jyoti%20spent%20the%20next%20two%20years%20being%20a%20doting%20mother.%20But%20the%20dream%20she%20harboured%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F258991%2Fcouple-quits-city-life-eco-friendly-homestay-banyan-bliss-ethnic-architecture%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erunning%20a%20homestay%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Udaipur%20had%20no%20intention%20of%20being%20silenced.%20%E2%80%9CIn%201999%2C%20I%20decided%20there%20was%20no%20better%20time%20than%20the%20present%20to%20make%20it%20happen.%20I%20returned%20to%20the%20land%20and%20this%20time%20I%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20going%20to%20let%20go%20of%20the%20plan.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20years%20leading%20up%20to%202004%2C%20when%20Devra%20officially%20started%20welcoming%20guests%2C%20Jyoti%20would%20make%20frequent%20trips%20between%20Delhi%2C%20where%20her%20husband%20and%20child%20were%2C%20and%20Udaipur%2C%20where%20her%20dream%20was.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThose%20years%20were%20beautiful%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20a%20journey%20of%20inking%20relationships%20with%20the%20craftsmen%20of%20the%20city%2C%20since%20architects%20and%20civil%20engineers%20were%20tough%20to%20find%20at%20the%20time.%20I%20got%20a%20local%20person%2C%20Shivji%2C%20on%20board%2C%20and%20he%20helped%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F280532%2Fchildhood-friends-convert-grandmothers-house-into-eco-friendly-homestay-maharashtra%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%