0as%20endocrine%20disruption%2C%20weight%20gain%2C%20insulin%20resistance%2C%20decreased%20reproductive%20health%2C%20cancer%2C%20among%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20data%20is%20scary.%20Based%20on%20our%20research%2C%20we%20understood%20that%20these%20cans%20should%20be%20disposed%20of%20after%2040%20times%20of%20use.%20Post%20that%2C%20they%20start%20losing%20their%20structural%20integrity.%20But%20the%20problem%20is%2C%20how%20to%20determine%20the%20number%20of%20times%20the%20can%20has%20been%20used%3F%20There%20is%20no%20tracking%2C%20there%20is%20no%20marker%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Bala.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Bharath%20(43)%20points%20out%20that%20people%20have%20come%20to%20accept%20these%20dirty%20cans%20as%20is.%20Nobody%20really%20questions%20it.%20%E2%80%9CWill%20you%20drink%20Ganga%20river%E2%80%99s%20water%20from%20a%20bathroom%20bucket%3F%20No.%20Likewise%2C%20we%20have%20accepted%20that%20these%20dirty%20plastic%20water%20cans%20are%20good.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20brothers%20wanted%20to%20use%20IoT%20tech%20to%20solve%20these%20problems%20and%20that%20is%20when%20their%20%E2%80%9Cconnected%20cans%E2%80%9D%20concept%20was%20born.%20In%202020%2C%20the%20siblings%20launched%20BookWater%20and%20were%20joined%20by%20Sameer%20and%20Hariharan%20about%20a%20year%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhat%20does%20the%20QR%20do%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20the%20brothers%20manufacture%20ISI%20(Indian%20Standards%20Institution)-rated%20plastic%20cans%20where%20they%20stick%20a%20QR%20code%20on%20every%20can.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20IoT%20sensors%20in%20the%20copackers%E2%80%99%20locations.%20Our%20sensors%20monitor%20the%20quality%20of%20water%20and%20where%20it%20is%20filled.%20If%20you%20order%20a%20can%20through%20the%20BookWater%20app%2C%20you%20can%20scan%20the%20QR%20code%20and%20quality%20reports%20will%20be%20visible%20to%20you%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Bharath.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%